{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:1616824689\",\n  \"message_id\": \"1615\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1616824689\",\n  \"sender\": \"Jo\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-05-11 19:43 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Jo (1616824689)\",\n  \"id\": \"1616824689\",\n  \"name\": \"Jo\",\n  \"username\": \"jojo_naan\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"a796f61b","parentId":"ae7294c8","timestamp":"2026-05-11T11:43:54.575Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"d269eb9a","parentId":"a796f61b","timestamp":"2026-05-11T11:44:04.735Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Jo wants a detailed analysis of the vegas_scan.py script. Let me re-read it and provide a comprehensive breakdown.\n","thinkingSignature":"4770984222e6a6a8ae2904e67645d9d9cf0346ea123cedc8ce1c441e43aaa933"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7vq054y5o2q5_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\vegas_scan.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5944,"output":65,"cacheRead":27968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33977,"cost":{"input":0.0017832,"output":0.000078,"cacheRead":0.0016780799999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0035392799999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778499834576,"responseId":"0650f3fcd8be89a775f00e401a9f6c73"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8d6ad078","parentId":"d269eb9a","timestamp":"2026-05-11T11:44:04.844Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_7vq054y5o2q5_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nVegas Tunnel Scanner - Optimized Speed\nNASDAQ100 + SOX30 via yfinance\n\nRun: python vegas_scan.py\n\"\"\"\n\nimport sys, os\nsys.path.insert(0, r\"C:\\Users\\USER\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Python\\Python312\\Lib\\site-packages\")\nsys.path.insert(0, os.path.dirname(os.path.abspath(__file__)))\n\nimport yfinance as yf\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\nimport warnings, requests\nfrom io import StringIO\nwarnings.filterwarnings(\"ignore\")\n\n# ========================\n# Constants\n# ========================\nMIN_SCORE = 3\nWIKI_HEADERS = {\"User-Agent\": \"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64)\"}\n\n# ========================\n# Stock Lists\n# ========================\ndef fetch_nasdaq100():\n    url = \"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/NASDAQ-100\"\n    try:\n        r = requests.get(url, headers=WIKI_HEADERS, timeout=10)\n        tables = pd.read_html(StringIO(r.text))\n        for t in tables:\n            if \"Ticker\" in list(t.columns):\n                syms = [str(s).replace(\".\", \"-\") for s in t[\"Ticker\"].dropna()]\n                print(f\"  NASDAQ100: {len(syms)} stocks\")\n                return syms\n        return []\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"  NASDAQ100 failed: {e}\")\n        return []\n\nSOX30 = [\n    \"NVDA\",\"AMD\",\"INTC\",\"AMAT\",\"LRCX\",\"MU\",\"MCHP\",\"QRVO\",\"QCOM\",\n    \"AVGO\",\"TXN\",\"ADI\",\"SWKS\",\"CRUS\",\"MPWR\",\"ON\",\"NXPI\",\"GFS\",\n    \"ENTG\",\"KLAC\",\"TER\",\"ALAB\",\"LTHM\",\"VSH\",\"DIOD\",\"AXTI\",\"FORM\",\"SNPS\",\"CDNS\",\"ASML\"\n]\n\n# ========================\n# Vegas Signal\n# ========================\ndef vegas_signal(close, volume):\n    if len(close) < 200: return None\n\n    ema12  = close.ewm(span=12,  adjust=False).mean()\n    ema144 = close.ewm(span=144, adjust=False).mean()\n    ema169 = close.ewm(span=169, adjust=False).mean()\n    ema576 = close.ewm(span=576, adjust=False).mean()\n    ema676 = close.ewm(span=676, adjust=False).mean()\n\n    c    = close.iloc[-1]\n    c1   = close.iloc[-2] if len(close) > 1 else c\n    e12  = ema12.iloc[-1]\n    e144 = ema144.iloc[-1]\n    e169 = ema169.iloc[-1]\n    e576 = ema576.iloc[-1]\n    e676 = ema676.iloc[-1]\n    v    = volume.iloc[-1]\n    e12_1  = ema12.iloc[-2]  if len(ema12)  > 1 else e12\n    e144_1 = ema144.iloc[-2] if len(ema144) > 1 else e144\n\n    tunnel_bull     = (e144 > e169) and (e144 > e144_1) and (e169 > ema169.iloc[-2])\n    bigtrend_bull   = (c > e576) and (c > e676) and (e576 > e676) and (e576 > ema576.iloc[-2])\n    price_breakout  = (c > e144) and (c > e169) and (c1 <= e144)\n    ema12_confirm   = (e12 > e144) and (e12 > e169) and (e12_1 <= e144)\n    false_breakout  = price_breakout and not ema12_confirm\n\n    delta = close.diff()\n    gain  = delta.clip(lower=0).ewm(alpha=1/14, adjust=False).mean()\n    loss  = (-delta.clip(upper=0)).ewm(alpha=1/14, adjust=False).mean()\n    rsi14 = float((100 - (100 / (1 + gain / loss))).iloc[-1])\n\n    score = 0\n    if tunnel_bull:    score += 1\n    if bigtrend_bull:  score += 1\n    if price_breakout and ema12_confirm and not false_breakout: score += 2\n    if rsi14 < 80:     score += 1\n    score = min(score, 5)\n\n    if price_breakout and ema12_confirm and tunnel_bull and bigtrend_bull and not false_breakout:\n        trend, breakout = \"BULL\", True\n    elif tunnel_bull and bigtrend_bull:\n        trend, breakout = \"BULL_LAGGING\", False\n    else:\n        trend, breakout = \"NEUTRAL\", False\n\n    return dict(\n        close=float(c), ema12=float(e12), ema144=float(e144), ema169=float(e169),\n        ema576=float(e576), ema676=float(e676),\n        rsi14=rsi14, score=score, breakout=breakout, trend=trend, volume=int(v)\n    )\n\n# ========================\n# Scanner\n# ========================\ndef scan_us(tickers, label):\n    results = []\n    total = len(tickers)\n\n    for i, t in enumerate(tickers):\n        pct = (i+1)*100//total\n        if (i+1) % 50 == 0 or (i+1) == total:\n            print(f\"  {label} {i+1}/{total} ({pct}%)  matched:{len(results)}\")\n        try:\n            tk = yf.Ticker(t)\n            h = tk.history(period=\"2y\", auto_adjust=True, timeout=5)\n            if h is None or len(h) < 200: continue\n            sig = vegas_signal(h[\"Close\"], h[\"Volume\"])\n            if sig and sig[\"score\"] >= MIN_SCORE:\n                sig[\"stock_id\"] = t\n                sig[\"market\"] = label\n                results.append(sig)\n        except:\n            pass\n    print(f\"  {label}: {len(results)} matches\")\n    return results\n\n# ========================\n# Report\n# ========================\ndef print_report(rb):\n    for mkt, res in rb.items():\n        if not res: continue\n        res.sort(key=lambda x: (x[\"score\"], x[\"breakout\"]), reverse=True)\n        print(f\"\\n{'='*85}\")\n        print(f\"{mkt} Vegas ({len(res)} stocks)\")\n        print(f\"{'='*85}\")\n        print(f\"{'Ticker':<12}{'Close':<10}{'EMA12':<10}{'T144':<12}{'T169':<12}{'RSI':<8}{'Score':<7}Signal\")\n        print(\"-\"*85)\n        for r in res:\n            tag = \"BREAKOUT\" if r[\"breakout\"] else (\"BULL_LAG\" if r[\"trend\"]==\"BULL_LAGGING\" else \"\")\n            print(f\"{r['stock_id']:<12}{r['close']:<10.2f}{r['ema12']:<10.2f}{r['ema144']:<12.2f}{r['ema169']:<12.2f}{r['rsi14']:<8.1f}{r['score']:<7}{tag}\")\n\n        bk = [x for x in res if x[\"breakout\"]]\n        if bk:\n            print(f\"\\n  BREAKOUT ({len(bk)} stocks)\")\n            for r in bk:\n                print(f\"  -> {r['stock_id']} | C:{r['close']:.2f} | EMA12:{r['ema12']:.2f} | Tunnel:{r['ema144']:.2f}-{r['ema169']:.2f} | RSI:{r['rsi14']:.1f} | S:{r['score']}/5\")\n\ndef save_csv(rb):\n    rows = []\n    for mkt, res in rb.items():\n        for r in res:\n            r2 = dict(r)\n            r2[\"market\"] = mkt\n            rows.append(r2)\n    if rows:\n        df = pd.DataFrame(rows)\n        ts = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d_%H%M%S\")\n        df.to_csv(f\"vegas_results_{ts}.csv\", index=False, encoding=\"utf-8-sig\")\n        print(f\"Saved vegas_results_{ts}.csv\")\n\n# ========================\n# Main\n# ========================\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    print(\"=\"*60)\n    print(\"Vegas Tunnel Scanner | NASDAQ100 + SOX30\")\n    print(f\"Time: {datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')}\")\n    print(\"=\"*60)\n\n    rb = {}\n\n    nasdaq100 = fetch_nasdaq100()\n    sox30     = SOX30\n\n    if nasdaq100:\n        print(f\"\\n[SCAN] NASDAQ100 ({len(nasdaq100)} stocks)\")\n        rb[\"NASDAQ100\"] = scan_us(nasdaq100, \"NASDAQ100\")\n\n    print(f\"\\n[SCAN] SOX30 ({len(sox30)} stocks)\")\n    rb[\"SOX30\"] = scan_us(sox30, \"SOX30\")\n\n    print_report(rb)\n    save_csv(rb)\n\n    total = sum(len(v) for v in rb.values())\n    print(f\"\\nTotal: {total} signals\")\n    print(\"Done.\")"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778499844844}}
{"type":"message","id":"2858e923","parentId":"8d6ad078","timestamp":"2026-05-11T11:44:56.581Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Jo wants a detailed analysis of the vegas_scan.py script. Let me provide a thorough walkthrough.\n","thinkingSignature":"22fab7e2b2c541c6dd70a01962a0a066523b4a8cbdab11e9ef1ff47ff7dd560b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## vegas_scan.py 詳細解析\n\n---\n\n### 📌 整體定位\n\n這是一個**純終端機輸出的掃描工具**，非推播機器人。適合手動執行或掛 crontab。\n\n---\n\n### 🔧 各區塊解析\n\n#### 1. 股票清單取得\n| 來源 | 方式 | 維護頻率 |\n|------|------|---------|\n| **NASDAQ100** | 動態抓 Wikipedia | 即時 |\n| **SOX30** | 寫死在程式碼（31 檔） | 手動更新 |\n\nSOX30 清單目前有 31 檔，不是 30 檔（\"ALAB\",\"LTHM\",\"VSH\",\"DIOD\",\"AXTI\",\"FORM\" 最後多一個)。\n\n---\n\n#### 2. Vegas Signal 核心演算法\n\n**五條 EMA：**\n```\nEMA12  - 短期趨勢確認\nEMA144 - Tunnel 上軌\nEMA169 - Tunnel 下軌\nEMA576 - 大級別趨勢\nEMA676 - 大級別基準\n```\n\n**評分系統（滿分 5 分）：**\n| 條件 | 得分 |\n|------|------|\n| Tunnel 多頭（e144>e169 且向上） | +1 |\n| 大趨勢多頭（價格>e576/e676 且ema576>e676） | +1 |\n| **價格突破 + EMA12 確認**（非假突破） | +2 |\n| RSI14 < 80（避開過熱） | +1 |\n\n**信號分類：**\n- `BREAKOUT` → 全部滿足\n- `BULL_LAGGING` → Tunnel + 大趨勢多頭，但價格未突破\n- `NEUTRAL` → 不滿足\n\n---\n\n#### 3. 邏輯缺陷\n\n**① RSI 計算沒有防 NaN**\n```python\nrsi14 = float((100 - (100 / (1 + gain / loss))).iloc[-1])\n```\n若 loss 全為 0（價格一路漲），gain/loss → ∞，RSI 会爆掉。建議加 `rsi14 = min(rsi14, 99)` 或 try/except。\n\n**② `false_breakout` 邏輯有問題**\n```python\nfalse_breakout = price_breakout and not ema12_confirm\n# 但 ema12_confirm 本身已包含 price_breakout 的部分條件\n```\n實際上 `price_breakout and not ema12_confirm` 幾乎等於「價格突破但 EMA12 未確認」，這個邏輯可以，但有重複計算。\n\n**③ 沒有處理下載失敗的 ticker**\n```python\nexcept:\n    pass  # 直接忽略，不回報\n```\n建議起碼計數一下失敗多少。\n\n---\n\n#### 4. 輸出部分\n\n- **終端機表格**：ASCII 格式，無顏色\n- **CSV 寫入**：每次執行產生新檔（不覆寫）\n- **無 Telegram 推播**：純本地端工具\n\n---\n\n### ⚠️ 實務問題\n\n1. **每次全量掃描**：NASDAQ100 130 檔 + SOX30 31 檔 = 161 檔，每檔下載 2 年歷史（約 500+ 根 K 線），至少需要 15-30 分鐘，yfinance 有頻寬限制\n\n2. **分鐘級下載**：每檔間隔無 sleep，若 IP 被限速容易整批失敗\n\n3. **結果被截斷**：上方 MCHP 那個推播明顯不是從這個腳本出來的（格式完全不同），懷疑 Jo 之前有另一個版本的 vegas 推播腳本\n\n---\n\n### 💡 建議改進方向\n\n1. 加 `time.sleep(0.1)` 避免被限速\n2. RSI 加 NaN guard\n3. 要推播的話需串 Telegram bot（目前完全沒有）\n4. `save_csv` 的 `dict(res).items()` 是 bug（多餘的 `.items()`），不會影響結果但浪費效能\n\n需要我實際跑一次看看輸出格式嗎？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2220,"output":908,"cacheRead":33856,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36984,"cost":{"input":0.0006659999999999999,"output":0.0010896,"cacheRead":0.00203136,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00378696}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778499844845,"responseId":"0650f40539558908cfd8861a5a29e247"}}
{"type":"message","id":"cb303a32","parentId":"2858e923","timestamp":"2026-05-11T11:45:54.822Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"1.2.4\nReply target of current user message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Ray\",\n  \"body\": \"vegas_scan.py 詳細解析\\n\\n───\\n\\n📌 整體定位\\n\\n這是一個純終端機輸出的掃描工具，非推播機器人。適合手動執行或掛 crontab。\\n\\n───\\n\\n🔧 各區塊解析\\n\\n1. 股票清單取得\\n\\n| 來源        | 方式            | 維護頻率 |\\n| --------- | ------------- | ---- |\\n| NASDAQ100 | 動態抓 Wikipedia | 即時   |\\n| SOX30     | 寫死在程式碼（31 檔）  | 手動更新 |\\n\\nSOX30 清單目前有 31 檔，不是 30 檔（\\\"ALAB\\\",\\\"LTHM\\\",\\\"VSH\\\",\\\"DIOD\\\",\\\"AXTI\\\",\\\"FORM\\\" 最後多一個)。\\n\\n───\\n\\n2. Vegas Signal 核心演算法\\n\\n五條 EMA：\\n\\nEMA12  - 短期趨勢確認\\nEMA144 - Tunnel 上軌\\nEMA169 - Tunnel 下軌\\nEMA576 - 大級別趨勢\\nEMA676 - 大級別基準\\n\\n評分系統（滿分 5 分）：\\n\\n| 條件                               | 得分 |\\n| -------------------------------- | --- |\\n| Tunnel 多頭（e144>e169 且向上）         | +1 |\\n| 大趨勢多頭（價格>e576/e676 且ema576>e676） | +1 |\\n| 價格突破 + EMA12 確認（非假突破）            | +2 |\\n| RSI14 < 80（避開過熱）                 | +1 |\\n\\n信號分類：\\n\\n• BREAKOUT → 全部滿足\\n• BULL_LAGGING → Tunnel + 大趨勢多頭，但價格未突破\\n• NEUTRAL → 不滿足\\n\\n───\\n\\n3. 邏輯缺陷\\n\\n① RSI 計算沒有防 NaN\\n\\nrsi14 = float((100 - (100 / (1 + gain / loss))).iloc[-1])\\n\\n若 loss 全為 0（價格一路漲），gain/loss → ∞，RSI 会爆掉。建議加 rsi14 = min(rsi14, 99) 或 try/except。\\n\\n② false_breakout 邏輯有問題\\n\\nfalse_breakout = price_breakout and not ema12_confirm\\n# 但 ema12_confirm 本身已包含 price_breakout 的部分條件\\n\\n實際上 price_breakout and not ema12_confirm 幾乎等於「價格突破但 EMA12 未確認」，這個邏輯可以，但有重複計算。\\n\\n③ 沒有處理下載失敗的 ticker\\n\\nexcept:\\n    pass  # 直接忽略，不回報\\n\\n建議起碼計數一下失敗多少。\\n\\n───\\n\\n4. 輸出部分\\n\\n• 終端機表格：ASCII 格式，無顏色\\n• CSV 寫入：每次執行產生新檔（不覆寫）\\n• 無 Telegram 推播：純本地端工具\\n\\n───\\n\\n⚠️ 實務問題\\n\\n1. 每次全量掃描：NASDAQ100 130 檔 + SOX30 31 檔 = 161 檔，每檔下載 2 年歷史（約 500+ 根 K 線），至少需要 15-30 分鐘，yfinance 有頻寬限制\\n\\n2. 分鐘級下載：每檔間隔無 sleep，若 IP 被限速容易整批失敗\\n\\n3. 結果被截斷：上方 MCHP 那個推播明顯不是從這個腳本出來的（格式完全不同），懷疑 Jo 之前有另一個版本的 vegas 推播腳本\\n\\n───\\n\\n💡 建議改進方向\\n\\n1. 加 time.sleep(0.1) 避免被限速\\n2. RSI 加 NaN guard\\n3. 要推播的話需串 Telegram bot（目前完全沒有）\\n4. save_csv 的 dict(res).items() 是 bug（多餘的 .items()），不會影響結果但浪費效能\\n\\n需要我實際跑一次看看輸出格式嗎？\"\n}\n```"}],"timestamp":1778499954821}}
