{"type":"message","id":"a40338cb","parentId":"c49c99e7","timestamp":"2026-05-11T11:47:37.875Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. Let me confirm what was fixed.\n","thinkingSignature":"87a863358405ab1169755044cdec60af087106e6c3b529bfaeafb4be21b8c444"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n已修正 4 點：\n\n| # | 問題 | 修法 |\n|---|------|------|\n| 1 | RSI 除零 / NaN | 加 try/except，fallback 50；clamp 0~99 |\n| 2 | 無 sleep 被限速 | 每檔加 `time.sleep(0.15)` |\n| 3 | 失敗不回報 | 新增 `failed` 清單，掃完顯示失敗數 |\n| 4 | `dict(res).items()` 多餘 | 改成 `for r in res` |\n\nSOX30 仍是 31 檔（寫死在程式碼）。如果要掛 cron 推播，還需要串 Telegram bot，目前純終端機輸出。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2420,"output":163,"cacheRead":38848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41431,"cost":{"input":0.000726,"output":0.00019559999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0023308799999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0032524799999999994}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778500049189,"responseId":"0650f4d2731bc0841febbb1cbac93ffc"}}
