{"type":"message","id":"a51261c0","parentId":"fad8f574","timestamp":"2026-05-11T11:48:06.330Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the vegas_v1_alpha team has several files. Let me read all the key files to understand the full system.\n","thinkingSignature":"bfb2c678490c8d5a8d270188d247f654b28ea01c2687faa2c2071f55afbb2b7b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qwcggzgfum1j_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\vegas_v1_alpha\\vegas_v1_live.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qwcggzgfum1j_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\vegas_v1_alpha\\tina_v3_core.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qwcggzgfum1j_3","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\vegas_v1_alpha\\tina_v3_scoring.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":195,"output":176,"cacheRead":40768,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41139,"cost":{"input":0.0000585,"output":0.00021119999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0024460799999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0027157799999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778500081620,"responseId":"0650f4f272887a79f2d866b49ddfb4f6"}}
{"type":"message","id":"aaf63285","parentId":"a51261c0","timestamp":"2026-05-11T11:48:06.340Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qwcggzgfum1j_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\nVegas V1 Alpha - 完整四階段交易引擎\nStep 1 日線環境 → Step 2 結構定位 → Step 3 精確觸發 → Step 4 動態風控\n\n對齊 Spec 要點：\n- Step 1: 日線隧道 + 斜率確認（EMA144 now > 5d ago）\n- Step 2: Fib 0.618 與小時隧道 EMA144/169 共振區（±0.5% 容差）\n- Step 3: J 線低位(<20)勾頭 + EMA12 站上 + MACD 柱狀體收縮\n- Step 4: ATR 2.0x 止損 / Fib 1.618 擴展目標 / 1.272 移動保本\n\nATR Stop 倍率說明：已從 3.0 改為 2.0（回測 2.0x 全部止損虧損，3.0x 止損頻率降低但延長持有，\n                          本系統以 EMA 169 作為底層支撐，2.0x 止損較為合理）\n\"\"\"\n\nimport sys\nimport os\nsys.path.insert(0, os.path.dirname(os.path.abspath(__file__)))\nsys.stdout.reconfigure(encoding='utf-8')\n\nimport time\nimport json\nimport warnings\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom typing import Optional, Dict, Tuple\n\nimport numpy as np\nimport pandas as pd\nimport yfinance as yf\nimport requests\n\nwarnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n\n# ===================== 設定區 =====================\nUNIVERSE = {\n    \"SP500\": [\"SPY\",\"IVV\",\"VOO\",\"VV\",\"SPEU\",\"EFA\",\"EEM\",\"AGG\",\"IEF\",\"TLT\",\"GLD\",\"SLV\",\"USO\",\"CPER\",\"DBA\",\"XLE\",\"XLF\",\"XLU\",\"XLI\",\"XLK\",\"XLV\",\"XLY\",\"XLP\",\"XLRE\",\"XLC\"],\n    \"NASDAQ100\": [\"QQQ\",\"QQQM\",\"TQQQ\",\"SQQQ\",\"QLD\",\"QID\",\"QLQD\",\"VGT\",\"ARKK\",\"ARKQ\",\"ARKW\",\"SOXX\",\"SMH\",\"SOXL\",\"SOXS\",\"CWEB\",\"DRN\",\"FINX\",\"EFIX\",\"XITK\"],\n    \"SOX30\": [\"AMAT\",\"LRCX\",\"MU\",\"NVDA\",\"ASML\",\"KLAC\",\"TSM\",\"INTC\",\"AMD\",\"QCOM\",\"AVGO\",\"MRVL\",\"MPWR\",\"ON\",\"MCHP\",\"TER\",\"ADI\",\"SWKS\",\"QRVO\",\"CRUS\",\"LSCC\",\"ENTG\",\"ALTR\"],\n}\n\nSYMBOLS = []\nfor _n, _l in UNIVERSE.items():\n    SYMBOLS.extend(_l)\nSYMBOLS = list(dict.fromkeys(SYMBOLS))  # 去重\n\nINTERVAL = \"1h\"\nDAILY_INTERVAL = \"1d\"\nATR_STOP = 2.0          # Spec ATR 2.0x（止損）\nATR_WARNING = 1.5       # ATR 1.5x（預警）\nMAX_HOLD_DAYS = 10\nVIX_MAX = 25\nFIB_ZONE_TOLERANCE = 0.005  # 0.5% 容差\nCONFLOW_TOLERANCE = 0.005   # 共振區容差\n\n\n# ===================== 工具函數 =====================\n\ndef calc_ema(close: np.ndarray, period: int) -> np.ndarray:\n    ema = np.zeros_like(close, dtype=float)\n    ema[0] = close[0]\n    alpha = 2.0 / (period + 1)\n    for i in range(1, len(close)):\n        ema[i] = close[i] * alpha + ema[i - 1] * (1 - alpha)\n    return ema\n\n\ndef calc_atr(high: np.ndarray, low: np.ndarray, close: np.ndarray, period: int = 14) -> np.ndarray:\n    tr = np.zeros(len(high), dtype=float)\n    prev_close = np.roll(close, 1)\n    prev_close[0] = close[0]\n    tr = np.maximum(high - low, np.maximum(np.abs(high - prev_close), np.abs(low - prev_close)))\n    atr = np.zeros(len(high), dtype=float)\n    atr[period - 1] = np.mean(tr[:period])\n    for i in range(period, len(atr)):\n        atr[i] = (atr[i - 1] * (period - 1) + tr[i]) / period\n    return atr\n\n\ndef calc_macd(close: np.ndarray, fast: int = 12, slow: int = 26, signal: int = 9) -> Tuple[np.ndarray, np.ndarray, np.ndarray]:\n    \"\"\"MACD: 標準 MACD Line / Signal Line / Histogram（柱狀體）\"\"\"\n    ema_fast = calc_ema(close, fast)\n    ema_slow = calc_ema(close, slow)\n    macd_line = ema_fast - ema_slow\n    signal_line = calc_ema(macd_line, signal)\n    histogram = macd_line - signal_line\n    return macd_line, signal_line, histogram\n\n\ndef calc_rsi(close: np.ndarray, period: int = 14) -> np.ndarray:\n    delta = np.diff(close, prepend=close[0])\n    gain = np.where(delta > 0, delta, 0.0)\n    loss = np.where(delta < 0, -delta, 0.0)\n    avg_gain = gain.copy()\n    avg_loss = loss.copy()\n    for i in range(1, len(avg_gain)):\n        avg_gain[i] = (avg_gain[i - 1] * (period - 1) + gain[i]) / period\n        avg_loss[i] = (avg_loss[i - 1] * (period - 1) + loss[i]) / period\n    rs = avg_gain / np.where(avg_loss == 0, 1e-10, avg_loss)\n    return 100 - (100 / (1 + rs))\n\n\ndef find_local_extrema(close: np.ndarray, order: int = 5) -> Tuple[np.ndarray, np.ndarray]:\n    close = np.asarray(close, dtype=float)\n    n = len(close)\n    maxima = np.zeros(n, dtype=bool)\n    minima = np.zeros(n, dtype=bool)\n    for i in range(order, n - order):\n        window = close[i - order:i + order + 1]\n        if close[i] == np.max(window):\n            maxima[i] = True\n        if close[i] == np.min(window):\n            minima[i] = True\n    return maxima, minima\n\n\n# ===================== 資料獲取 =====================\ndef fetch_hourly_data(symbol: str, period: str = \"30d\") -> pd.DataFrame:\n    try:\n        df = yf.Ticker(symbol).history(period=period, interval=INTERVAL, auto_adjust=True)\n        if df is None or len(df) < 144:\n            print(f\"[警告] {symbol} 1h 資料不足（{len(df) if df is not None else 0} 筆）\")\n        df.columns = [c.title() for c in df.columns]\n        return df\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"[抓取 1h 失敗] {e}\")\n        return pd.DataFrame()\n\n\ndef fetch_daily_data(symbol: str, period: str = \"2y\") -> pd.DataFrame:\n    try:\n        df = yf.Ticker(symbol).history(period=period, interval=DAILY_INTERVAL, auto_adjust=True)\n        if df is None or len(df) < 170:\n            print(f\"[警告] {symbol} 日線資料不足（{len(df) if df is not None else 0} 筆）\")\n        df.columns = [c.title() for c in df.columns]\n        return df\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"[抓取日線失敗] {e}\")\n        return pd.DataFrame()\n\n\ndef fetch_vix() -> float:\n    try:\n        df = yf.Ticker(\"^VIX\").history(period=\"5d\", interval=\"1d\")\n        return float(df['Close'].iloc[-1]) if df is not None and not df.empty else 20.0\n    except:\n        return 20.0\n\n\n# ===================== 小時線指標 =====================\ndef calculate_hourly_indicators(df: pd.DataFrame) -> dict:\n    if len(df) < 169:\n        return {}\n    close = df['Close'].values.astype(float)\n    high = df['High'].values.astype(float)\n    low = df['Low'].values.astype(float)\n\n    ema12 = calc_ema(close, 12)\n    ema144 = calc_ema(close, 144)\n    ema169 = calc_ema(close, 169)\n    atr = calc_atr(high, low, close, 14)\n    macd_line, signal_line, histogram = calc_macd(close, 12, 26, 9)\n\n    # KDJ 自實作\n    n = 9\n    k = np.zeros_like(close)\n    d = np.zeros_like(close)\n    for i in range(n - 1, len(close)):\n        low_n = np.min(low[i - n + 1:i + 1])\n        high_n = np.max(high[i - n + 1:i + 1])\n        if high_n == low_n:\n            k[i] = 50\n            d[i] = 50\n        else:\n            k[i] = (close[i] - low_n) / (high_n - low_n) * 100\n            d[i] = np.mean(k[max(n, i - n + 1):i + 1])\n    j = 3 * k - 2 * d\n\n    return {\n        'close': close, 'high': high, 'low': low,\n        'ema12': ema12, 'ema144': ema144, 'ema169': ema169,\n        'atr': atr, 'k': k, 'd': d, 'j': j,\n        'macd_hist': histogram,\n        'dates': df.index.tolist()\n    }\n\n\n# ===================== 日線指標 =====================\ndef calculate_daily_indicators(df: pd.DataFrame) -> dict:\n    if len(df) < 170:\n        return {}\n    close = df['Close'].values.astype(float)\n    high = df['High'].values.astype(float)\n    low = df['Low'].values.astype(float)\n\n    ema144 = calc_ema(close, 144)\n    ema169 = calc_ema(close, 169)\n    atr = calc_atr(high, low, close, 14)\n    atr_pct = atr / close * 100\n    rsi = calc_rsi(close, 14)\n\n    return {\n        'close': close, 'high': high, 'low': low,\n        'ema144': ema144, 'ema169': ema169,\n        'atr': atr, 'atr_pct': atr_pct, 'rsi': rsi,\n        'dates': df.index.tolist()\n    }\n\n\n# ===================== Fib 結構 + 共振區檢測（Step 2）=====================\ndef get_fib618_with_confluence(df_h: pd.DataFrame, h_ind: dict, order: int = 5) -> Optional[dict]:\n    \"\"\"\n    計算 Fib 0.618 並檢查是否與小時隧道 EMA144/169 重疊（共振區）。\n    同時計算 Fib 1.618 擴展目標價。\n    \"\"\"\n    if len(df_h) < 50:\n        return None\n\n    close = df_h['Close'].values.astype(float)\n    maxima, minima = find_local_extrema(close, order=order)\n\n    peak_idx = np.where(maxima)[0]\n    valley_idx = np.where(minima)[0]\n\n    if len(peak_idx) < 2 or len(valley_idx) < 2:\n        return None\n\n    # 取最近 4 個轉折點，找最近一個波段（低點到高點或高點到低點）\n    pivots = []\n    for idx in sorted(list(peak_idx) + list(valley_idx))[-4:]:\n        pivots.append((idx, close[idx]))\n    pivots.sort(key=lambda x: x[0])\n\n    if len(pivots) < 2:\n        return None\n\n    p1_close = pivots[-2][1]\n    p2_close = pivots[-1][1]\n    high_val = max(p1_close, p2_close)\n    low_val = min(p1_close, p2_close)\n    diff = high_val - low_val\n\n    # Fib 0.618 回撤位\n    if p2_close > p1_close:  # 上升波段：回撤用 high - 0.618*diff\n        fib_618 = high_val - 0.618 * diff\n        # Fib 1.618 擴展目標（從 low 往上算）\n        target = low_val + 1.618 * diff\n    else:  # 下降波段：反彈用 low + 0.618*diff\n        fib_618 = low_val + 0.618 * diff\n        # Fib 1.618 擴展目標（從 high 往下算）— 目標在下方的版本\n        target = high_val - 1.618 * diff\n        # 若是反彈波，目標變成上方 high + 1.618*diff，修正：\n        target = high_val + 1.618 * diff\n\n    # Step 2 共振區檢查：fib_618 是否落在 EMA144/169 隧道區間 ±0.5%\n    h_ema144 = h_ind['ema144'][-1]\n    h_ema169 = h_ind['ema169'][-1]\n    tunnel_upper = max(h_ema144, h_ema169)\n    tunnel_lower = min(h_ema144, h_ema169)\n\n    confluent = (tunnel_lower * (1 - CONFLOW_TOLERANCE) <= fib_618 <= tunnel_upper * (1 + CONFLOW_TOLERANCE))\n\n    return {\n        'fib_618': float(fib_618),\n        'target': float(target),\n        'confluent': confluent,\n        'tunnel_upper': float(tunnel_upper),\n        'tunnel_lower': float(tunnel_lower),\n        'is_rally': p2_close > p1_close\n    }\n\n\n# ===================== Telegram =====================\nTG_TOKEN = \"872054…qAiY\"\nTG_CHAT_ID = \"1616824689\"\n\n\ndef send_telegram(msg: str):\n    url = f\"https://api.telegram.org/bot{TG_TOKEN}/sendMessage\"\n    try:\n        requests.post(url, data={\"chat_id\": TG_CHAT_ID, \"text\": msg, \"parse_mode\": \"Markdown\"}, timeout=10)\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"[TG 失敗] {e}\")\n\n\n# ===================== 主邏輯：四階段過濾 =====================\ndef execute_logic(symbol: str) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"\n    四階段引擎：\n    Step 1: 日線隧道（多頭 + 斜率）\n    Step 2: 小時線 Fib 618 共振區\n    Step 3: J 線低位勾頭 + EMA12 站上 + MACD 柱狀體\n    Step 4: ATR 2.0x 止損 / Fib 1.618 目標\n    \"\"\"\n\n    # ── 抓資料 ──\n    vix = fetch_vix()\n    df_hourly = fetch_hourly_data(symbol, \"30d\")\n    df_daily = fetch_daily_data(symbol, \"2y\")\n\n    if df_hourly.empty or df_daily.empty:\n        print(f\"[{symbol}] 資料失敗\")\n        return False\n\n    h_ind = calculate_hourly_indicators(df_hourly)\n    d_ind = calculate_daily_indicators(df_daily)\n\n    if not h_ind or not d_ind or len(df_daily) < 170:\n        print(f\"[{symbol}] 指標失敗\")\n        return False\n\n    if len(h_ind['close']) < 170:\n        print(f\"[{symbol}] 小時線資料不足，無法計算 EMA169\")\n        return False\n\n    # ── 最新數值 ──\n    d1_close = d_ind['close'][-1]\n    d1_ema144 = d_ind['ema144'][-1]\n    d1_ema169 = d_ind['ema144'][-1]  # 避免取到同一個，先用 ema144\n    d1_ema169 = d_ind['ema169'][-1]\n    d5_ema144 = d_ind['ema144'][-6] if len(d_ind['ema144']) >= 6 else d_ind['ema144'][-1]\n\n    h1_close = h_ind['close'][-1]\n    h1_low = h_ind['low'][-1]\n    h1_ema12 = h_ind['ema12'][-1]\n    h1_ema144 = h_ind['ema144'][-1]\n    h1_ema169 = h_ind['ema169'][-1]\n    h1_atr = h_ind['atr'][-1]\n    h1_j = h_ind['j'][-1]\n    h2_j = h_ind['j'][-2]\n    h3_j = h_ind['j'][-3] if len(h_ind['j']) >= 3 else h2_j\n    h1_macd_hist = h_ind['macd_hist'][-1]\n    h2_macd_hist = h_ind['macd_hist'][-2]\n\n    d1_rsi = d_ind['rsi'][-1]\n    d1_atr = d_ind['atr'][-1]\n\n    # ── Step 1: 日線環境（多頭 + 隧道斜率）──\n    daily_trend_ok = (d1_close > d1_ema144) and (d1_close > d1_ema169)\n    tunnel_slope_ok = d1_ema144 > d5_ema144  # EMA144 現在 > 5 天前\n    step1_pass = daily_trend_ok and tunnel_slope_ok\n\n    if not step1_pass:\n        print(f\"[{symbol}] Step1 否決 | 日線多頭:{daily_trend_ok} | 隧道斜率:{tunnel_slope_ok}\")\n        return False\n\n    # ── Step 2: 小時線結構定位 + 共振區 ──\n    fib = get_fib618_with_confluence(df_hourly, h_ind, order=5)\n    step2_ready = fib is not None\n    is_in_zone = fib and (h1_low <= fib['fib_618'] * (1 + FIB_ZONE_TOLERANCE))\n    confluent_bonus = fib and fib['confluent']  # 高勝率標記，不阻擋進場\n\n    if not step2_ready:\n        print(f\"[{symbol}] Step2 否決 | 無有效 Fib 結構\")\n        return False\n\n    # ── Step 3: 精確觸發（J 低位勾頭 + EMA12 + MACD）──\n    # J 線從低位（< 30）向上勾頭，代表動能耗竭後反轉\n    j_in_low_before = h2_j < 30  # 轉身前 J 在低位區\n    j_bullish_turn = (h1_j > h2_j) and j_in_low_before  # J 由低轉高\n    price_above_ema12 = h1_close > h1_ema12\n    macd_strengthening = (h1_macd_hist > h2_macd_hist) or (h1_macd_hist > 0 and h2_macd_hist <= 0)\n\n    step3_pass = j_bullish_turn and price_above_ema12 and macd_strengthening\n\n    if not step3_pass:\n        print(f\"[{symbol}] Step3 否決 | J低位勾頭:{j_bullish_turn} | EMA12站上:{price_above_ema12} | MACD轉強:{macd_strengthening}\")\n        return False\n\n    # ── Step 4: 風控計算 ──\n    dynamic_sl = h1_ema169 - h1_atr * ATR_STOP          # ATR 2.0x 止損\n    warning_sl = h1_ema169 - h1_atr * ATR_WARNING       # ATR 1.5x 預警\n    target_price = fib['target']\n\n    # 1.272 移動保本檢查：當價格 > 進場價 + 1.272*ATR，建議將止損移至保本\n    entry_price = h1_close\n    break_even_trigger = entry_price + 1.272 * h1_atr\n\n    msg = (\n        f\"🚀 *Vegas V1 Alpha 進場訊號*\\n\"\n        f\"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n\"\n        f\"📌 標的: `{symbol}`\\n\"\n        f\"💰 現價: `${h1_close:.2f}`\\n\"\n        f\"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n\"\n        f\"*【四階段核查】*\\n\"\n        f\"✅ Step1 日線環境：多頭 + 隧道斜率向上\\n\"\n        f\"✅ Step2 Fib618 共振區：`${fib['fib_618']:.2f}` 落在隧道區間\\n\"\n        f\"✅ Step3 動能觸發：J 線低位(<20)勾頭 + 站上 EMA12 + MACD 轉強\\n\"\n        f\"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n\"\n        f\"*【風控】*\\n\"\n        f\"🛡️ 動態止損: `${dynamic_sl:.2f}` (ATR×{ATR_STOP})\\n\"\n        f\"⚠️ 預警線: `${warning_sl:.2f}` (ATR×{ATR_WARNING})\\n\"\n        f\"🎯 獲利目標: `${target_price:.2f}` (Fib 1.618 擴展)\\n\"\n        f\"📈 保本觸發價: `${break_even_trigger:.2f}` (1.272×ATR)\\n\"\n        f\"⏱ 持有上限: `{MAX_HOLD_DAYS}` 天\\n\"\n        f\"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n\"\n        f\"_VIX:{vix:.1f} | RSI:{d1_rsi:.1f} | 隧道:[{fib['tunnel_lower']:.1f}-{fib['tunnel_upper']:.1f}]_\"\n    )\n    send_telegram(msg)\n    print(f\"[{symbol}] ✅ 四階段全數通過，訊號已發送\")\n    return True\n\n\n# ===================== 主程式 =====================\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    print(f\"[{datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')}] Vegas V1 Alpha 四階段引擎啟動 | {len(SYMBOLS)} 檔\")\n    print(f\"[邏輯] ATR Stop={ATR_STOP}x / Warning={ATR_WARNING}x / Fib Target=1.618 / Confluence Zone\")\n    print(\"-\" * 60)\n    while True:\n        ts = datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')\n        hits = []\n        for sym in SYMBOLS:\n            try:\n                if execute_logic(sym):\n                    hits.append(sym)\n            except Exception as e:\n                print(f\"[{sym}] 錯誤: {e}\")\n        if hits:\n            print(f\"[{ts}] 🚀 觸發: {', '.join(hits)}\")\n        else:\n            print(f\"[{ts}] 本輪無訊號（{len(SYMBOLS)}檔）\")\n        print(f\"[{ts}] 等待 1 小時...\")\n        print(\"-\" * 60)\n        time.sleep(3600)\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778500086339}}
{"type":"message","id":"c7d333a4","parentId":"aaf63285","timestamp":"2026-05-11T11:48:06.340Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qwcggzgfum1j_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\r\n\"\"\"\r\nVegas V1 Alpha Pro - Core System\r\nMulti-timeframe mean-reversion momentum system for US stocks\r\n\r\nCore components:\r\n- EMA 144/169 tunnel (hourly trigger + daily environment filter)\r\n- KDJ J-cross momentum trigger\r\n- ATR 2x dynamic stop-loss\r\n- Fib 618 structured pivot points (numpy-based local extrema)\r\n- 1000-point scoring engine\r\n\r\nNO external dependencies beyond: numpy, pandas, yfinance, ta\r\n\"\"\"\r\n\r\nimport sys\r\nimport os\r\nsys.path.insert(0, os.path.dirname(os.path.abspath(__file__)))\r\nsys.stdout.reconfigure(encoding='utf-8')\r\n\r\nimport sqlite3\r\nimport json\r\nimport math\r\nimport warnings\r\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\r\nfrom typing import Optional, Dict, List, Tuple\r\n\r\nimport numpy as np\r\nimport pandas as pd\r\nimport yfinance as yf\r\n\r\nwarnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\r\n\r\n# ===================== PATH CONFIG =====================\r\nSCRIPT_DIR = os.path.dirname(os.path.abspath(__file__))\r\n# tina_v3_core.py is at teams/vegas_v1_alpha/tina_v3_core.py\r\n# Navigate up: teams/vegas_v1_alpha -> teams -> <root>\r\nTEAM_DIR = os.path.join(SCRIPT_DIR)\r\nROOT_DIR = os.path.normpath(os.path.join(SCRIPT_DIR, '..', '..'))\r\nDB_PATH = os.path.join(ROOT_DIR, 'data', 'us_history.db')\r\nos.makedirs(TEAM_DIR, exist_ok=True)\r\n\r\n\r\n# ===================== UTILITY: numpy EMA =====================\r\ndef calc_ema(close: np.ndarray, period: int) -> np.ndarray:\r\n    \"\"\"Calculate EMA using numpy (no pandas_ta needed).\"\"\"\r\n    ema = np.zeros_like(close, dtype=float)\r\n    ema[0] = close[0]\r\n    alpha = 2.0 / (period + 1)\r\n    for i in range(1, len(close)):\r\n        ema[i] = close[i] * alpha + ema[i-1] * (1 - alpha)\r\n    return ema\r\n\r\n\r\ndef calc_rsi(close: np.ndarray, period: int = 14) -> np.ndarray:\r\n    \"\"\"Calculate RSI using ta library (already available).\"\"\"\r\n    try:\r\n        import ta\r\n        rsi = ta.momentum.RSIIndicator(close, window=period).rsi()\r\n        return rsi\r\n    except:\r\n        delta = np.diff(close, prepend=close[0])\r\n        gain = np.where(delta > 0, delta, 0.0)\r\n        loss = np.where(delta < 0, -delta, 0.0)\r\n        avg_gain = gain.copy()\r\n        avg_loss = loss.copy()\r\n        for i in range(1, len(avg_gain)):\r\n            avg_gain[i] = (avg_gain[i-1] * (period-1) + gain[i]) / period\r\n            avg_loss[i] = (avg_loss[i-1] * (period-1) + loss[i]) / period\r\n        rs = avg_gain / np.where(avg_loss == 0, 1e-10, avg_loss)\r\n        rsi = 100 - (100 / (1 + rs))\r\n        return rsi\r\n\r\n\r\ndef calc_atr(high: np.ndarray, low: np.ndarray, close: np.ndarray, period: int = 14) -> np.ndarray:\r\n    \"\"\"Calculate ATR using ta library.\"\"\"\r\n    try:\r\n        import ta\r\n        atr = ta.volatility.AverageTrueRange(high, low, close, window=period).average_true_range()\r\n        return atr\r\n    except:\r\n        tr = np.zeros(len(high), dtype=float)\r\n        prev_close = np.roll(close, 1)\r\n        prev_close[0] = close[0]\r\n        tr = np.maximum(high - low, np.maximum(np.abs(high - prev_close), np.abs(low - prev_close)))\r\n        atr = np.zeros(len(high), dtype=float)\r\n        atr[period-1] = np.mean(tr[:period])\r\n        for i in range(period, len(atr)):\r\n            atr[i] = (atr[i-1] * (period-1) + tr[i]) / period\r\n        return atr\r\n\r\n\r\ndef calc_kdj(high: np.ndarray, low: np.ndarray, close: np.ndarray,\r\n             n: int = 9, d_n: int = 3, m2: int = 3) -> Tuple[np.ndarray, np.ndarray, np.ndarray]:\r\n    \"\"\"Calculate KDJ using ta library (StochasticOscillator).\r\n    Uses n=9 (fast K period), d_n=3 (slow D period, also J calculation param).\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    try:\r\n        import ta\r\n        import pandas as pd\r\n        close_s = pd.Series(close)\r\n        high_s = pd.Series(high)\r\n        low_s = pd.Series(low)\r\n        kdj = ta.momentum.StochasticOscillator(high_s, low_s, close_s, n=n, d_n=d_n)\r\n        k = kdj.stoch().values\r\n        d = kdj.stoch_signal().values\r\n        j = 3 * k - 2 * d  # %J = 3*K - 2*D\r\n        return k, d, j\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return np.zeros_like(close), np.zeros_like(close), np.zeros_like(close)\r\n\r\n\r\ndef find_local_extrema(close: np.ndarray, order: int = 5) -> Tuple[np.ndarray, np.ndarray]:\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    Find local maxima and minima using numpy (scipy-free equivalent of scipy.signal.argrelextrema).\r\n    Returns boolean arrays of same length as close.\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    close = np.asarray(close, dtype=float)\r\n    n = len(close)\r\n    maxima = np.zeros(n, dtype=bool)\r\n    minima = np.zeros(n, dtype=bool)\r\n    \r\n    for i in range(order, n - order):\r\n        window = close[i-order:i+order+1]\r\n        if close[i] == np.max(window):\r\n            maxima[i] = True\r\n        if close[i] == np.min(window):\r\n            minima[i] = True\r\n    \r\n    return maxima, minima\r\n\r\n\r\ndef find_fib618_pivots(close: np.ndarray, order: int = 5) -> Tuple[Optional[float], Optional[float]]:\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    Find Fib 618 pivot points from weekly data.\r\n    Returns (support_price, resistance_price) based on recent swing low/high near 61.8% retracement.\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    maxima, minima = find_local_extrema(close, order=order)\r\n    if not np.any(maxima) or not np.any(minima):\r\n        return None, None\r\n    \r\n    highs_idx = np.where(maxima)[0]\r\n    lows_idx = np.where(minima)[0]\r\n    if len(highs_idx) < 2 or len(lows_idx) < 2:\r\n        return None, None\r\n    \r\n    recent_highs = close[highs_idx[-5:]] if len(highs_idx) >= 5 else close[highs_idx]\r\n    recent_lows = close[lows_idx[-5:]] if len(lows_idx) >= 5 else close[lows_idx]\r\n    \r\n    swing_high = np.max(recent_highs)\r\n    swing_low = np.min(recent_lows)\r\n    \r\n    # Fib 618 retracement levels\r\n    range_val = swing_high - swing_low\r\n    fib618_support = swing_high - range_val * 0.618\r\n    fib618_resistance = swing_low + range_val * 0.618\r\n    \r\n    return float(fib618_support), float(fib618_resistance)\r\n\r\n\r\n# ===================== DATA FETCH =====================\r\ndef fetch_weekly_data(symbol: str, period: str = '6mo') -> pd.DataFrame:\r\n    \"\"\"Fetch weekly OHLCV for structure analysis.\"\"\"\r\n    try:\r\n        ticker = yf.Ticker(symbol)\r\n        df = ticker.history(period=period, interval='1wk', auto_adjust=True)\r\n        if df is None or len(df) < 20:\r\n            return pd.DataFrame()\r\n        df.columns = [c.title() for c in df.columns]\r\n        return df\r\n    except:\r\n        return pd.DataFrame()\r\n\r\n\r\ndef fetch_daily_data(symbol: str, period: str = '3mo') -> pd.DataFrame:\r\n    \"\"\"Fetch daily OHLCV for environment filter.\"\"\"\r\n    try:\r\n        ticker = yf.Ticker(symbol)\r\n        df = ticker.history(period=period, interval='1d', auto_adjust=True)\r\n        if df is None or len(df) < 30:\r\n            return pd.DataFrame()\r\n        df.columns = [c.title() for c in df.columns]\r\n        return df\r\n    except:\r\n        return pd.DataFrame()\r\n\r\n\r\ndef fetch_hourly_data(symbol: str, period: str = '5d') -> pd.DataFrame:\r\n    \"\"\"Fetch hourly OHLCV for trigger layer.\"\"\"\r\n    try:\r\n        ticker = yf.Ticker(symbol)\r\n        df = ticker.history(period=period, interval='1h', auto_adjust=True)\r\n        if df is None or len(df) < 20:\r\n            return pd.DataFrame()\r\n        df.columns = [c.title() for c in df.columns]\r\n        return df\r\n    except:\r\n        return pd.DataFrame()\r\n\r\n\r\ndef load_symbols_from_db() -> List[str]:\r\n    \"\"\"Load all US stock symbols from local DB.\"\"\"\r\n    conn = sqlite3.connect(DB_PATH)\r\n    cur = conn.cursor()\r\n    cur.execute('SELECT DISTINCT symbol FROM daily_ohlcv ORDER BY symbol')\r\n    symbols = [r[0] for r in cur.fetchall()]\r\n    conn.close()\r\n    return symbols\r\n\r\n\r\n# ===================== INDICATORS =====================\r\ndef calculate_daily_indicators(df: pd.DataFrame) -> Dict:\r\n    \"\"\"Calculate daily indicators: EMA144, EMA169, RSI, ATR.\"\"\"\r\n    if len(df) < 170:\r\n        return {}\r\n    close = df['Close'].values.astype(float)\r\n    high = df['High'].values.astype(float)\r\n    low = df['Low'].values.astype(float)\r\n    \r\n    ema144 = calc_ema(close, 144)\r\n    ema169 = calc_ema(close, 169)\r\n    rsi = calc_rsi(close, 14)\r\n    atr = calc_atr(high, low, close, 14)\r\n    atr_pct = atr / close * 100\r\n    \r\n    return {\r\n        'close': close,\r\n        'high': high,\r\n        'low': low,\r\n        'ema144': ema144,\r\n        'ema169': ema169,\r\n        'rsi': rsi,\r\n        'atr': atr,\r\n        'atr_pct': atr_pct,\r\n        'dates': df.index.tolist()\r\n    }\r\n\r\n\r\ndef calculate_hourly_indicators(df: pd.DataFrame) -> Dict:\r\n    \"\"\"Calculate hourly indicators: EMA144, EMA169, KDJ J-cross.\"\"\"\r\n    if len(df) < 170:\r\n        return {}\r\n    close = df['Close'].values.astype(float)\r\n    high = df['High'].values.astype(float)\r\n    low = df['Low'].values.astype(float)\r\n    \r\n    ema144 = calc_ema(close, 144)\r\n    ema169 = calc_ema(close, 169)\r\n    k, d, j = calc_kdj(high, low, close, 9, 3, 3)\r\n    \r\n    return {\r\n        'close': close,\r\n        'high': high,\r\n        'low': low,\r\n        'ema144': ema144,\r\n        'ema169': ema169,\r\n        'k': k,\r\n        'd': d,\r\n        'j': j,\r\n        'dates': df.index.tolist()\r\n    }\r\n\r\n\r\ndef calculate_weekly_structure(df: pd.DataFrame) -> Dict:\r\n    \"\"\"Calculate weekly Fib 618 structure.\"\"\"\r\n    if len(df) < 30:\r\n        return {}\r\n    close = df['Close'].values.astype(float)\r\n    support, resistance = find_fib618_pivots(close, order=5)\r\n    return {\r\n        'close': close,\r\n        'fib618_support': support,\r\n        'fib618_resistance': resistance,\r\n        'dates': df.index.tolist()\r\n    }\r\n\r\n\r\n# ===================== SIGNAL GENERATION =====================\r\ndef generate_entry_signal(symbol: str, verbose: bool = False) -> Optional[Dict]:\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    Generate entry signal for a symbol using multi-timeframe analysis.\r\n    Returns signal dict or None if no signal.\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    daily = fetch_daily_data(symbol, '3mo')\r\n    hourly = fetch_hourly_data(symbol, '5d')\r\n    weekly = fetch_weekly_data(symbol, '6mo')\r\n    \r\n    if daily.empty or hourly.empty:\r\n        return None\r\n    \r\n    d_ind = calculate_daily_indicators(daily)\r\n    h_ind = calculate_hourly_indicators(hourly)\r\n    w_str = calculate_weekly_structure(weekly)\r\n    \r\n    if not d_ind or not h_ind:\r\n        return None\r\n    \r\n    # === DAILY ENVIRONMENT FILTER ===\r\n    d_close = d_ind['close']\r\n    d_ema144 = d_ind['ema144']\r\n    d_ema169 = d_ind['ema169']\r\n    d_rsi = d_ind['rsi']\r\n    d_atr_pct = d_ind['atr_pct']\r\n    \r\n    n = len(d_close)\r\n    d_env_ok = (d_ema144[n-1] > d_ema169[n-1]) and (d_close[n-1] > d_ema144[n-1])\r\n    \r\n    # === HOURLY TRIGGER ===\r\n    h_close = h_ind['close']\r\n    h_ema144 = h_ind['ema144']\r\n    h_ema169 = h_ind['ema169']\r\n    h_j = h_ind['j']\r\n    h_k = h_ind['k']\r\n    h_d = h_ind['d']\r\n    \r\n    h_n = len(h_close)\r\n    \r\n    # Check EMA144 cross above EMA169 in last 4 bars\r\n    ema_cross_bull = False\r\n    for i in range(max(0, h_n-5), h_n):\r\n        if i >= 1:\r\n            if h_ema144[i] > h_ema169[i] and h_ema144[i-1] <= h_ema169[i-1]:\r\n                ema_cross_bull = True\r\n                break\r\n    \r\n    # Check KDJ J-cross above K and D\r\n    kdj_bull = False\r\n    for i in range(max(0, h_n-4), h_n):\r\n        if i >= 1:\r\n            if h_j[i] > h_k[i] and h_j[i] > h_d[i] and h_j[i-1] <= h_k[i-1]:\r\n                kdj_bull = True\r\n                break\r\n    \r\n    # === FIB 618 STRUCTURE ===\r\n    fib_ok = False\r\n    current_price = d_close[n-1]\r\n    if w_str.get('fib618_support'):\r\n        support = w_str['fib618_support']\r\n        if support and abs(current_price - support) / support < 0.05:\r\n            fib_ok = True\r\n    \r\n    # === ENTRY CONDITIONS (all must be true) ===\r\n    if not (d_env_ok and ema_cross_bull and kdj_bull):\r\n        return None\r\n    \r\n    if d_rsi[n-1] > 70:\r\n        return None  # overbought\r\n    \r\n    # Calculate entry score\r\n    score = score_stock(symbol, d_ind, h_ind, w_str)\r\n    \r\n    entry = {\r\n        'symbol': symbol,\r\n        'entry_price': float(current_price),\r\n        'atr': float(d_ind['atr'][n-1]),\r\n        'atr_pct': float(d_atr_pct[n-1]),\r\n        'daily_rsi': float(d_rsi[n-1]),\r\n        'daily_ema144': float(d_ema144[n-1]),\r\n        'daily_ema169': float(d_ema169[n-1]),\r\n        'ema_cross': ema_cross_bull,\r\n        'kdj_cross': kdj_bull,\r\n        'fib618_ok': fib_ok,\r\n        'score': score,\r\n        'stop_loss': float(current_price - 3 * d_ind['atr'][n-1]),\r\n        'target': float(current_price + 2 * d_ind['atr'][n-1]),\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    if verbose:\r\n        print(f\"  [{symbol}] Signal: price={current_price:.2f}, RSI={d_rsi[n-1]:.1f}, \"\r\n              f\"EMA_cross={ema_cross_bull}, KDJ_cross={kdj_bull}, score={score}\")\r\n    \r\n    return entry\r\n\r\n\r\n# ===================== SCORING ENGINE =====================\r\ndef score_stock(symbol: str, d_ind: Dict, h_ind: Dict, w_str: Dict) -> int:\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    1000-point scoring system.\r\n    Returns score 0-1000.\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    score = 0\r\n    n = len(d_ind['close'])\r\n    \r\n    # === MOMENTUM SCORE (0-300) ===\r\n    close = d_ind['close']\r\n    \r\n    # 1-month momentum (% change over 21 trading days)\r\n    lookback_1m = min(21, n-1)\r\n    momentum_1m = (close[n-1] / close[n-1-lookback_1m] - 1) * 100 if n > lookback_1m else 0\r\n    \r\n    # 1-week momentum (% change over 5 trading days)\r\n    lookback_1w = min(5, n-1)\r\n    momentum_1w = (close[n-1] / close[n-1-lookback_1w] - 1) * 100 if n > lookback_1w else 0\r\n    \r\n    # Volume ratio (current volume / 20-day average) - requires volume column\r\n    # Skipping volume scoring for simplicity (would need volume data)\r\n    \r\n    # Score: 1-month momentum\r\n    if momentum_1m >= 10: mom_1m_score = 120\r\n    elif momentum_1m >= 5: mom_1m_score = 90\r\n    elif momentum_1m >= 2: mom_1m_score = 60\r\n    elif momentum_1m >= 0: mom_1m_score = 30\r\n    else: mom_1m_score = 0\r\n    \r\n    # Score: 1-week momentum\r\n    if momentum_1w >= 5: mom_1w_score = 100\r\n    elif momentum_1w >= 2: mom_1w_score = 70\r\n    elif momentum_1w >= 0: mom_1w_score = 40\r\n    else: mom_1w_score = 10\r\n    \r\n    momentum_score = mom_1m_score + mom_1w_score  # max 220, but cap at 300\r\n    \r\n    # === TREND STRENGTH (0-200) ===\r\n    d_ema144 = d_ind['ema144']\r\n    d_ema169 = d_ind['ema169']\r\n    d_close = d_ind['close']\r\n    \r\n    # Daily EMA alignment (0-120)\r\n    if d_ema144[n-1] > d_ema169[n-1]:\r\n        ema_alignment_score = 60\r\n    else:\r\n        ema_alignment_score = 0\r\n    \r\n    # Price above EMA144 (0-60)\r\n    if d_close[n-1] > d_ema144[n-1]:\r\n        price_above_ema = 30\r\n    else:\r\n        price_above_ema = 0\r\n    \r\n    # === ATR VOLATILITY SCORE (0-200) ===\r\n    atr_pct = d_ind['atr_pct']\r\n    current_atr_pct = atr_pct[n-1] if not np.isnan(atr_pct[n-1]) else 1.0\r\n    \r\n    if 0.5 <= current_atr_pct <= 2.0:\r\n        atr_score = 200\r\n    elif 0.3 <= current_atr_pct < 0.5:\r\n        atr_score = 150\r\n    elif 2.0 < current_atr_pct <= 3.5:\r\n        atr_score = 120\r\n    elif current_atr_pct < 0.3:\r\n        atr_score = 80\r\n    else:\r\n        atr_score = 60\r\n    \r\n    # === INSTITUTIONAL FLOW (0-150) ===\r\n    # TODO: Integrate T86 data when available\r\n    inst_score_val = 75  # Neutral score when no data\r\n    \r\n    # === STRUCTURE SCORE (0-150) ===\r\n    current_price = d_close[n-1]\r\n    struct_score = 0\r\n    \r\n    if w_str.get('fib618_support'):\r\n        support = w_str['fib618_support']\r\n        if support:\r\n            # Within 3% of Fib 618 support\r\n            if abs(current_price - support) / support < 0.03:\r\n                struct_score += 80\r\n            elif abs(current_price - support) / support < 0.05:\r\n                struct_score += 40\r\n    \r\n    # Pivot quality (local extrema strength)\r\n    maxima, minima = find_local_extrema(d_close, order=5)\r\n    n_maxima = np.sum(maxima)\r\n    n_minima = np.sum(minima)\r\n    if n_maxima >= 3 and n_minima >= 3:\r\n        struct_score += 70\r\n    elif n_maxima >= 2 and n_minima >= 2:\r\n        struct_score += 35\r\n    \r\n    total = min(1000, momentum_score + ema_alignment_score + price_above_ema + atr_score + inst_score_val + struct_score)\r\n    \r\n    return int(total)\r\n\r\n\r\n# ===================== UNIVERSE SCAN =====================\r[... 14188 more characters truncated]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778500086339}}
{"type":"message","id":"243a6616","parentId":"c7d333a4","timestamp":"2026-05-11T11:48:06.341Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qwcggzgfum1j_3","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\nTina V3 Alpha Pro - Scoring Engine\n1000-point multi-factor scoring system for US stocks\n\nComponent scores:\n- Momentum Score (0-300): 1-month momentum, 1-week momentum\n- Trend Strength (0-200): EMA alignment, price position\n- ATR Volatility-Adjusted Score (0-200): Position sizing hint\n- Institutional Flow (0-150): T86 data integration\n- Structure Score (0-150): Fib 618 proximity, pivot quality\n\"\"\"\n\nimport numpy as np\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom typing import Dict, Tuple, Optional, List\n\n\n# ===================== SCORE COMPONENT WEIGHTS =====================\nDEFAULT_WEIGHTS = {\n    'momentum_w': 0.30,\n    'trend_w': 0.25,\n    'atr_w': 0.20,\n    'inst_w': 0.10,\n    'struct_w': 0.15,\n}\n\n\n# ===================== MOMENTUM SCORE (0-300) =====================\ndef calc_momentum_score(close: np.ndarray, n: int) -> Tuple[int, Dict]:\n    lookback_1m = min(21, n-1)\n    lookback_1w = min(5, n-1)\n    \n    momentum_1m = (close[n-1] / close[n-1-lookback_1m] - 1) * 100 if n > lookback_1m else 0\n    momentum_1w = (close[n-1] / close[n-1-lookback_1w] - 1) * 100 if n > lookback_1w else 0\n    \n    if momentum_1m >= 15: mom_1m_score = 120\n    elif momentum_1m >= 10: mom_1m_score = 100\n    elif momentum_1m >= 7: mom_1m_score = 80\n    elif momentum_1m >= 5: mom_1m_score = 60\n    elif momentum_1m >= 3: mom_1m_score = 40\n    elif momentum_1m >= 1: mom_1m_score = 20\n    else: mom_1m_score = 0\n    \n    if momentum_1w >= 8: mom_1w_score = 100\n    elif momentum_1w >= 5: mom_1w_score = 80\n    elif momentum_1w >= 3: mom_1w_score = 60\n    elif momentum_1w >= 2: mom_1w_score = 40\n    elif momentum_1w >= 0: mom_1w_score = 20\n    else: mom_1w_score = 0\n    \n    lookback_3m = min(63, n-1)\n    momentum_3m = (close[n-1] / close[n-1-lookback_3m] - 1) * 100 if n > lookback_3m else 0\n    if momentum_3m >= 20: mom_3m_score = 80\n    elif momentum_3m >= 15: mom_3m_score = 60\n    elif momentum_3m >= 10: mom_3m_score = 40\n    elif momentum_3m >= 5: mom_3m_score = 20\n    else: mom_3m_score = 0\n    \n    total = min(300, mom_1m_score + mom_1w_score + mom_3m_score)\n    \n    return total, {\n        'mom_1m': momentum_1m, 'mom_1m_score': mom_1m_score,\n        'mom_1w': momentum_1w, 'mom_1w_score': mom_1w_score,\n        'mom_3m': momentum_3m, 'mom_3m_score': mom_3m_score,\n    }\n\n\n# ===================== TREND STRENGTH (0-200) =====================\ndef calc_trend_score(close: np.ndarray, ema144: np.ndarray, ema169: np.ndarray, n: int) -> Tuple[int, Dict]:\n    score = 0\n    subs = {}\n    \n    if ema144[n-1] > ema169[n-1]:\n        score += 60\n        subs['ema_aligned'] = True\n    else:\n        score += 0\n        subs['ema_aligned'] = False\n    \n    if close[n-1] > ema144[n-1]:\n        score += 40\n        subs['price_above_ema144'] = True\n    else:\n        score += 0\n        subs['price_above_ema144'] = False\n    \n    if close[n-1] > ema169[n-1]:\n        score += 30\n        subs['price_above_ema169'] = True\n    else:\n        score += 0\n        subs['price_above_ema169'] = False\n    \n    if n >= 6:\n        slope = (ema144[n-1] - ema144[n-6]) / 5\n        slope_pct = slope / ema144[n-6] * 100 if ema144[n-6] > 0 else 0\n        if slope_pct >= 0.5: score += 30\n        elif slope_pct >= 0.2: score += 20\n        elif slope_pct >= 0: score += 10\n        subs['ema_slope_pct'] = slope_pct\n    else:\n        subs['ema_slope_pct'] = 0\n    \n    deviation = abs(close[n-1] - ema144[n-1]) / ema144[n-1] * 100\n    if deviation <= 5: score += 40\n    elif deviation <= 10: score += 20\n    subs['ema_deviation_pct'] = deviation\n    \n    total = min(200, score)\n    return total, subs\n\n\n# ===================== ATR VOLATILITY SCORE (0-200) =====================\ndef calc_atr_score(atr_pct: np.ndarray, n: int) -> Tuple[int, Dict]:\n    current_atr_pct = atr_pct[n-1] if not np.isnan(atr_pct[n-1]) and atr_pct[n-1] > 0 else 1.0\n    \n    if 0.5 <= current_atr_pct <= 2.5:\n        atr_score = 200\n    elif 0.3 <= current_atr_pct < 0.5:\n        atr_score = 150\n    elif 2.5 < current_atr_pct <= 4.0:\n        atr_score = 120\n    elif current_atr_pct < 0.3:\n        atr_score = 80\n    else:\n        atr_score = 60\n    \n    if n >= 14:\n        atr_trend = atr_pct[n-1] / np.nanmean(atr_pct[n-14:n-1]) if np.nanmean(atr_pct[n-14:n-1]) > 0 else 1.0\n    else:\n        atr_trend = 1.0\n    \n    subs = {\n        'atr_pct': current_atr_pct,\n        'atr_trend': atr_trend,\n        'atr_regime': 'high' if current_atr_pct > 3 else ('low' if current_atr_pct < 0.5 else 'normal')\n    }\n    \n    return atr_score, subs\n\n\n# ===================== INSTITUTIONAL FLOW SCORE (0-150) =====================\ndef calc_institutional_score(inst_foreign: float, inst_trust: float) -> Tuple[int, Dict]:\n    if inst_foreign > 5000:\n        foreign_score = 75\n    elif inst_foreign > 2000:\n        foreign_score = 60\n    elif inst_foreign > 1000:\n        foreign_score = 45\n    elif inst_foreign > 0:\n        foreign_score = 30\n    elif inst_foreign > -1000:\n        foreign_score = 15\n    else:\n        foreign_score = 0\n    \n    if inst_trust > 3000:\n        trust_score = 75\n    elif inst_trust > 1000:\n        trust_score = 60\n    elif inst_trust > 500:\n        trust_score = 45\n    elif inst_trust > 0:\n        trust_score = 30\n    elif inst_trust > -500:\n        trust_score = 15\n    else:\n        trust_score = 0\n    \n    total = min(150, foreign_score + trust_score)\n    \n    return total, {\n        'foreign_net': inst_foreign, 'foreign_score': foreign_score,\n        'trust_net': inst_trust, 'trust_score': trust_score,\n    }\n\n\n# ===================== STRUCTURE SCORE (0-150) =====================\ndef _find_local_extrema(c: np.ndarray, order: int = 5) -> Tuple[np.ndarray, np.ndarray]:\n    \"\"\"Internal: find local maxima/minima using numpy.\"\"\"\n    n = len(c)\n    maxima = np.zeros(n, dtype=bool)\n    minima = np.zeros(n, dtype=bool)\n    for i in range(order, n - order):\n        window = c[i-order:i+order+1]\n        if c[i] == np.max(window):\n            maxima[i] = True\n        if c[i] == np.min(window):\n            minima[i] = True\n    return maxima, minima\n\n\ndef calc_structure_score(close: np.ndarray, fib618_support: Optional[float],\n                         fib618_resistance: Optional[float], n: int) -> Tuple[int, Dict]:\n    score = 0\n    current_price = close[n-1]\n    subs = {}\n    \n    if fib618_support:\n        deviation = abs(current_price - fib618_support) / fib618_support\n        if deviation < 0.02:\n            score += 80\n            subs['fib618_zone'] = 'tight'\n        elif deviation < 0.03:\n            score += 60\n            subs['fib618_zone'] = 'near'\n        elif deviation < 0.05:\n            score += 40\n            subs['fib618_zone'] = 'approaching'\n        else:\n            subs['fib618_zone'] = 'far'\n    else:\n        subs['fib618_zone'] = 'no_data'\n    \n    if fib618_resistance:\n        deviation_r = abs(current_price - fib618_resistance) / fib618_resistance\n        if deviation_r < 0.03:\n            score += 20\n        elif deviation_r < 0.05:\n            score += 10\n        subs['resistance_zone'] = 'near' if deviation_r < 0.05 else 'far'\n    else:\n        subs['resistance_zone'] = 'no_data'\n    \n    maxima, minima = _find_local_extrema(close, order=5)\n    n_maxima = int(np.sum(maxima))\n    n_minima = int(np.sum(minima))\n    \n    if n_maxima >= 4 and n_minima >= 4:\n        score += 30\n        subs['pivot_quality'] = 'high'\n    elif n_maxima >= 3 and n_minima >= 3:\n        score += 20\n        subs['pivot_quality'] = 'medium'\n    elif n_maxima >= 2 and n_minima >= 2:\n        score += 10\n        subs['pivot_quality'] = 'low'\n    else:\n        subs['pivot_quality'] = 'poor'\n    \n    total = min(150, score)\n    return total, subs\n\n\n# ===================== MAIN SCORING =====================\ndef score_stock_full(d_ind: Dict, h_ind: Dict, w_str: Dict,\n                     inst_foreign: float = 0, inst_trust: float = 0,\n                     weights: Dict = None) -> Dict:\n    if weights is None:\n        weights = DEFAULT_WEIGHTS.copy()\n    \n    n = len(d_ind['close'])\n    \n    mom_score, mom_subs = calc_momentum_score(d_ind['close'], n)\n    trend_score, trend_subs = calc_trend_score(d_ind['close'], d_ind['ema144'], d_ind['ema169'], n)\n    atr_score, atr_subs = calc_atr_score(d_ind['atr_pct'], n)\n    inst_score, inst_subs = calc_institutional_score(inst_foreign, inst_trust)\n    struct_score, struct_subs = calc_structure_score(\n        d_ind['close'], w_str.get('fib618_support'), w_str.get('fib618_resistance'), n)\n    \n    raw_total = mom_score + trend_score + atr_score + inst_score + struct_score\n    \n    result = {\n        'total_score': min(1000, raw_total),\n        'momentum_score': mom_score,\n        'trend_score': trend_score,\n        'atr_score': atr_score,\n        'institutional_score': inst_score,\n        'structure_score': struct_score,\n        'sub_components': {\n            'momentum': mom_subs,\n            'trend': trend_subs,\n            'atr': atr_subs,\n            'institutional': inst_subs,\n            'structure': struct_subs,\n        }\n    }\n    \n    score = result['total_score']\n    if score >= 700:\n        result['signal'] = 'APPROVE'\n        result['position_size'] = '5%'\n    elif score >= 500:\n        result['signal'] = 'CAUTION'\n        result['position_size'] = '2.5%'\n    else:\n        result['signal'] = 'REJECT'\n        result['position_size'] = '0%'\n    \n    return result\n\n\n# ===================== CALIBRATION REPORT =====================\ndef generate_calibration_report(trades: List[Dict], weights: Dict) -> str:\n    if not trades:\n        return \"No trades for calibration.\"\n    \n    df = pd.DataFrame(trades)\n    wr = len(df[df['profit_pct'] > 0]) / len(df) * 100\n    avg = df['profit_pct'].mean()\n    \n    report_lines = [\n        \"=\" * 60,\n        \"TINA V3 ALPHA - SCORE CALIBRATION REPORT\",\n        \"=\" * 60,\n        f\"Weight Configuration:\",\n        f\"  Momentum:     {weights['momentum_w']*100:.0f}%\",\n        f\"  Trend:        {weights['trend_w']*100:.0f}%\",\n        f\"  ATR:          {weights['atr_w']*100:.0f}%\",\n        f\"  Institutional: {weights['inst_w']*100:.0f}%\",\n        f\"  Structure:   {weights['struct_w']*100:.0f}%\",\n        \"\",\n        f\"Backtest Results:\",\n        f\"  Win Rate:    {wr:.1f}%\",\n        f\"  Avg Return: {avg:.2f}%\",\n        f\"  Total Trades: {len(df)}\",\n        \"=\" * 60,\n    ]\n    \n    return \"\\n\".join(report_lines)\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778500086340}}
{"type":"message","id":"4f874bb3","parentId":"243a6616","timestamp":"2026-05-11T11:48:13.366Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me read the remaining files to get a complete picture.\n","thinkingSignature":"e340d4f3f472197e6e342346f6fd073adc723ffb9fc07c2b56c2c48ba6c277c0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5oj3hnapd4nl_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\vegas_v1_alpha\\tina_v3_sop.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5oj3hnapd4nl_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\vegas_v1_alpha\\_run_live_scan.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":17290,"output":114,"cacheRead":40960,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58364,"cost":{"input":0.005187,"output":0.0001368,"cacheRead":0.0024576,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0077814}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778500086342,"responseId":"0650f4f76fefadf9807cd37d6042ed2a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f12026cf","parentId":"4f874bb3","timestamp":"2026-05-11T11:48:13.376Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_5oj3hnapd4nl_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Tina V3 Alpha Pro v3.1 - Standard Operating Procedure\n## Multi-Timeframe Mean-Reversion Momentum System for US Stocks\n\n---\n\n## 1. System Overview\n\n**Version:** v3.1 Alpha Pro (2026-05-10)\n**Paradigm:** Trend-following momentum system (complementary to Nana's mean-reversion)\n**Universe:** US stocks (154 symbols from local DB)\n**Timeframe:** Multi-timeframe (hourly trigger → daily filter → weekly structure)\n\n### 1.1 Core Philosophy\n\nTina V3 Alpha Pro identifies momentum-driven entries using:\n1. **Hourly EMA tunnel crossover** (144/169) as the primary trigger\n2. **KDJ J-cross** as momentum confirmation\n3. **Daily EMA alignment** as environment filter\n4. **Fib 618 pivots** as structural support framework\n5. **ATR 3x dynamic stop-loss** (widened from 2x to avoid noise)\n\nThis system is **not a replacement** for Nana. It complements by catching sustained momentum moves rather than reversal bounces.\n\n### 1.2 Key Changes in v3.1\n\n| Parameter | v3.0 | v3.1 | Reason |\n|-----------|:----:|:----:|:-------|\n| ATR Stop | 2x | **3x** | 2x was too tight, 100% of 2x stops were losers |\n| Target | 3x | **2x** | Faster profit-taking, reduce exposure |\n| Max Hold | 15d | **10d** | Reduce market exposure |\n| RSI Entry | <70 | **<65** | More selective entry |\n| Entry Score | ≥200 | **≥350** | Reduce false signals |\n| Backtest Period | 2024+ | **2026 Mar-Apr** | Focus on recent data |\n\n---\n\n## 2. Scoring Rubric (1000 Points)\n\n### 2.1 Score Breakdown\n\n| Component | Max Points | Sub-factors |\n|-----------|-----------|-------------|\n| **Momentum Score** | 300 | 1-month (0-120), 1-week (0-100), momentum bonus (0-80) |\n| **Trend Strength** | 200 | EMA alignment (0-60), Price>EMA144 (0-30), structure (0-110) |\n| **ATR Volatility** | 200 | ATR% regime (0-200) |\n| **Institutional Flow** | 150 | T86 foreign/trust flow (0-75 + 0-75) |\n| **Structure Score** | 150 | Fib 618 proximity (0-80), pivot quality (0-70) |\n| **TOTAL** | **1000** | |\n\n### 2.2 Signal Thresholds\n\n| Score | Signal | Position Size | Action |\n|-------|--------|---------------|--------|\n| **700-1000** | **APPROVE** | 5% of portfolio | Enter full size |\n| **500-699** | **CAUTION** | 2.5% of portfolio | Enter half size |\n| **350-499** | **WATCH** | 1% | Small probe, tight stop |\n| **< 350** | **REJECT** | 0% | Skip |\n\n### 2.3 Score Calibration (v3.1 Backtest Results)\n\n| Component | Default Weight | Calibrated | Notes |\n|-----------|---------------|-----------|-------|\n| Momentum | 30% | **35%** | Most predictive in backtest |\n| Trend | 25% | **25%** | Stable |\n| ATR | 20% | **15%** | Reduced — ATR stops were losers |\n| Institutional | 10% | **10%** | T86 data integration pending |\n| Structure | 15% | **15%** | Stable |\n\n---\n\n## 3. Entry Rules\n\n### 3.1 Entry Conditions (ALL must be true)\n\n```\n✅ Daily EMA tunnel aligned:\n   Daily EMA144 > Daily EMA169  AND  Price > Daily EMA144\n\n✅ Hourly EMA crossover:\n   Hourly EMA144 crosses above Hourly EMA169 (within last 4 hours)\n\n✅ KDJ J-cross triggered:\n   J-line crosses above K and D simultaneously (within last 4 hours)\n\n✅ Fib 618 structure:\n   Price within ±3% of identified Fib 618 support pivot\n\n✅ RSI condition:\n   Stock RSI (14) < 65 (tightened from <70)\n\n✅ Score threshold:\n   Score >= 350 (raised from 200)\n\n✅ VIX filter (market context):\n   VIX < 25 (no extreme panic)\n```\n\n### 3.2 Entry Steps\n\n1. **Daily Filter Check** (09:30 ET)\n   - Scan universe, filter by Daily EMA alignment\n   - Identify candidates passing environment filter\n\n2. **Hourly Trigger Monitoring** (every hour)\n   - Watch for EMA 144/169 crossover on hourly chart\n   - Confirm with KDJ J-cross\n\n3. **Structure Validation**\n   - Verify price near Fib 618 support\n   - Check pivot quality\n\n4. **Score Calculation**\n   - Run 1000-point scoring\n   - If score >= 350, generate entry signal\n\n5. **Position Sizing**\n   - Score 700+: 5% position\n   - Score 500-699: 2.5% position\n   - Score 350-499: 1% position (tight stop)\n   - Max 3 concurrent positions\n\n---\n\n## 4. Exit Rules\n\n### 4.1 Exit Triggers (ANY triggers exit)\n\n| Exit | Condition | Priority |\n|------|-----------|----------|\n| **ATR 3x Stop** | Price drops 3× ATR from entry | 1 (hard stop) |\n| **Hold Timeout** | 10 trading days max hold | 2 |\n| **Target Hit** | Price reaches 2× ATR profit | 3 |\n| **MA Cross** | Hourly EMA144 crosses below EMA169 | 4 |\n\n### 4.2 Exit Priority\n\n1. **ATR 3x stop** is non-negotiable — execute immediately\n2. **Hold timeout** — close at end of day 10\n3. **Target hit** — close 50%, move stop to breakeven\n4. **MA cross** — close remaining position\n\n### 4.3 Exit Reason Distribution (v3.1 Backtest)\n\n| Exit Reason | Count | Win Rate | Avg Return |\n|-------------|-------|----------|------------|\n| hold_max | 58 | 62.1% | +1.12% |\n| target_hit | 29 | 100.0% | +4.43% |\n| atr_stop | 11 | 0.0% | -5.85% |\n| ma_cross | 2 | 50.0% | +0.31% |\n\n**Insight:** ATR 3x stops still cause 100% loss rate, but much less frequent (11 vs 5 previously). Consider tightening further if loss rate remains 100%.\n\n---\n\n## 5. Position Sizing Guidelines\n\n### 5.1 Score-Based Position Sizing\n\n| Score | Position Size (% of Portfolio) | Max Concurrent |\n|-------|--------------------------------|----------------|\n| 700-1000 | 5% | 3 positions |\n| 500-699 | 2.5% | 3 positions |\n| 350-499 | 1% | 2 positions |\n| < 350 | 0% (skip) | — |\n\n### 5.2 Risk Limits\n\n| Limit | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| Per-trade max loss | -10% (3x ATR typically covers) |\n| Total portfolio risk | -15% (all positions) |\n| Max concurrent | 3 positions |\n| Max single position | 5% |\n\n---\n\n## 6. Daily Operational Checklist\n\n### 6.1 Daily (09:30 ET) — Daily Filter Scan\n\n```\n- [ ] Check VIX (must be < 25)\n- [ ] Scan universe for Daily EMA alignment candidates\n- [ ] Calculate 1000-point scores for top candidates\n- [ ] Filter by score >= 350\n- [ ] Identify APPROVE/CAUTION/WATCH signals\n- [ ] Update watchlist for hourly monitoring\n- [ ] Report top 5 signals to Telegram\n```\n\n### 6.2 Hourly (:00) — Trigger Monitoring\n\n```\n- [ ] Monitor hourly EMA 144/169 crossover\n- [ ] Confirm with KDJ J-cross\n- [ ] Validate Fib 618 proximity\n- [ ] Execute entry if all conditions met + score >= 350\n- [ ] If entry: calculate ATR-based stop and target\n- [ ] Log entry with timestamp and score\n```\n\n### 6.3 Weekly (Saturday 10:00) — Full Review\n\n```\n- [ ] Run full universe scan\n- [ ] Execute sandbox backtest on test symbols\n- [ ] Calibrate scoring weights\n- [ ] Review exit reason distribution\n- [ ] Update SOP if needed\n- [ ] Generate weekly performance report\n```\n\n---\n\n## 7. Backtest Metrics (v3.1 - Mar-Apr 2026 Focus)\n\n### 7.1 Primary Metrics\n\n| Metric | Target | v3.0 Result | v3.1 Result | Status |\n|--------|--------|-------------|-------------|--------|\n| Win Rate (WR) | >55% | 68.4% | **60.0%** | ✅ 達標 |\n| Average Return | >2.0% | 1.64% | **0.99%** | ❌ 未達標 |\n| Max Drawdown | <10% | -20.18% | **-16.47%** | ❌ 超標 |\n| Sharpe-like | >0.3 | 0.264 | **0.233** | ⚠️ 待優化 |\n| False Signal Rate | <30% | 31.6% | **46.0%** | ❌ 超標 |\n\n### 7.2 Per-Stock Breakdown (v3.1)\n\n| Symbol | Trades | Win Rate | Avg Return |\n|--------|--------|----------|------------|\n| AAPL | 29 | 58.6% | +1.07% |\n| MSFT | 32 | 59.4% | +1.04% |\n| CRM | 15 | 66.7% | +1.22% |\n| GOOGL | 24 | 58.3% | +0.60% |\n\n### 7.3 False Signal Definition\n\nA **false signal** is any entry that generates < 0.5% profit before exit (regardless of exit reason).\nv3.1: 46/100 trades were false signals — this is the key issue to address.\n\n---\n\n## 8. Scoring Weight Calibration\n\n### 8.1 Calibration Triggers\n\n- Run calibration after every 50+ trades\n- Weight changes require ≥ 55% win rate validation\n- Max weight shift per calibration: ±10%\n\n### 8.2 Current Weights (v3.1)\n\n| Component | Weight | Range |\n|-----------|--------|-------|\n| Momentum | 35% | 25-45% |\n| Trend | 25% | 15-35% |\n| ATR | 15% | 10-25% |\n| Institutional | 10% | 5-20% |\n| Structure | 15% | 10-25% |\n\n---\n\n## 9. Cron Schedule\n\n### 9.1 Cron Jobs\n\n| Job ID | Name | Schedule | Mode | Script | Purpose |\n|--------|------|----------|------|--------|---------|\n| tina_v3_daily | V3 Daily Scan | `0 9 * * 1-5` (09:00 ET weekdays) | Auto Think | tina_v3_core.py | Daily filter scan + signal report |\n| tina_v3_weekly | V3 Weekly Review | `0 10 * * 6` (Sat 10:00 ET) | Full Think | tina_v3_core.py | Full universe scan + calibration |\n| tina_v3_hourly | V3 Hourly Trigger | `0 * * * *` (hourly) | Fast Track | tina_v3_core.py | Trigger layer monitoring |\n| tina_v3_backtest | V3 Backtest | `0 11 * * 6` (Sat 11:00 ET) | Auto | run_backtest.py | Sandbox backtest run |\n\n### 9.2 Time Zone Note\n\nET = America/New_York timezone. Cron expressions are written in ET local time.\n\n---\n\n## 10. System Architecture\n\n```\nteams/tina_v3_alpha/\n├── tina_v3_core.py       # Main system (orchestration)\n├── tina_v3_scoring.py    # 1000-point scoring engine\n├── tina_v3_sop.md        # This SOP\n├── tina_v3_design.md     # Design document\n├── sandbox_v31.json      # v3.1 backtest results\n└── run_backtest.py       # Backtest runner\n\nData Sources:\n├── Local DB: data/us_history.db (154 symbols, daily_ohlcv)\n├── yfinance API: live hourly/daily fetch\n└── TWSE T86: institutional flow (when available)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 11. Key Differences from Nana\n\n| Aspect | Nana v5.28 | Tina V3 Alpha v3.1 |\n|--------|-----------|---------------------|\n| **Paradigm** | Mean-reversion | Trend-following |\n| **Entry trigger** | RSI 30-45 | EMA 144/169 + KDJ + Score≥350 |\n| **Holding period** | 3 days | 5-10 days |\n| **Exit** | RSI overbought / hold max | ATR 3x / target 2x / MA cross |\n| **Universe** | TW stocks | US stocks |\n| **Scoring** | Manual tier system | 1000-point automated |\n| **RSI role** | Primary entry filter (RSI 30-45) | Secondary filter (RSI <65) |\n\n---\n\n## 12. Known Issues & TODOs\n\n| Priority | Issue | Status |\n|----------|-------|--------|\n| HIGH | False signal rate 46% (target <30%) | Needs filter tightening |\n| HIGH | ATR 3x stops still 100% loss rate | Consider 2.5x or add VIX filter |\n| MED | Institutional flow (T86) not integrated | Pending |\n| MED | Entry score threshold may need further tuning | Monitor false signals |\n| LOW | Fib 618 structure not fully validated in backtest | Needs weekly data integration |\n\n---\n\n_This SOP is the official operating guide for Tina V3 Alpha Pro v3.1._\n_Last Updated: 2026-05-10 17:56 GMT+8_"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778500093376}}
{"type":"message","id":"e034152c","parentId":"f12026cf","timestamp":"2026-05-11T11:48:13.377Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_5oj3hnapd4nl_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\nimport sys, os, importlib, warnings\nwarnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n\nsys.path.insert(0, os.path.abspath('.'))\nmod = importlib.import_module('vegas_v1_live')\n\nfrom datetime import datetime\nts = datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')\nhits = []\nfails = []\n\nSYMBOLS = mod.SYMBOLS\nfor sym in SYMBOLS:\n    try:\n        if mod.execute_logic(sym):\n            hits.append(sym)\n    except Exception as e:\n        fails.append(f'{sym}:{e}')\n\nif hits:\n    msg = f\"📡 *Vegas V1 Alpha 定時掃描 {ts}*\\n\"\n    msg += f\"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n\"\n    msg += f\"🚀 觸發進場：{', '.join(hits)}\\n\"\n    msg += f\"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n\"\n    msg += f\"失敗:{len(fails)} 檔 | 總掃描:{len(SYMBOLS)} 檔\"\n    mod.send_telegram(msg)\n    print(msg)\nelse:\n    print(f'[{ts}] 本輪無訊號 ({len(SYMBOLS)}檔)')"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778500093376}}
{"type":"message","id":"13efae58","parentId":"e034152c","timestamp":"2026-05-11T11:49:40.203Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a comprehensive picture of the Vegas V1 Alpha system. Let me write a detailed analysis.\n","thinkingSignature":"d4469f1556ddf6674377ce866006da8516314d6859e82f54a19c98ab070b22d7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## Vegas V1 Alpha 完整解析\n\n---\n\n### 📁 腳本架構（5 支）\n\n| 腳本 | 角色 | 核心功能 |\n|------|------|---------|\n| `vegas_v1_live.py` | **主引擎** | 四階段過濾 + Telegram 推播 |\n| `tina_v3_core.py` | **Pro 版核心** | 1000 分評分系統 + 回測引擎 |\n| `tina_v3_scoring.py` | **評分模組** | 五因子評分（動量/趨勢/ATR/機構/結構） |\n| `tina_v3_sop.md` | **操作手冊** | v3.1 參數/規則/回測數據 |\n| `_run_live_scan.py` | **定時包裝** | 輪詢 SYMBOLS 並發送 Telegram 摘要 |\n\n---\n\n### 🔴 vegas_v1_live.py（推播腳本）\n\n**四階段邏輯：**\n\n```\nStep 1 日線環境過濾\n  ✅ price > EMA144 AND price > EMA169\n  ✅ EMA144[today] > EMA144[5day ago]  （隧道向上）\n\nStep 2 小時線結構定位\n  ✅ Fib 0.618 迴撤位存在\n  ✅ 現價低點 ≤ Fib618 × 1.005  （進入 Zone）\n  ✅ Fib618 落在 EMA144/169 隧道 ±0.5%  （共振加分）\n\nStep 3 精確觸發\n  ✅ J 由低（<30）向上勾頭（低位反轉）\n  ✅ 現價 > EMA12\n  ✅ MACD 柱狀體擴大 或 由負轉正\n\nStep 4 風控計算\n  🛡️ 動態止損 = EMA169 - ATR×2.0\n  ⚠️ 預警線   = EMA169 - ATR×1.5\n  🎯 目標價   = Fib 1.618 擴展\n  📈 保本觸發 = 進場價 + ATR×1.272\n```\n\n**UNIVERSE 定義：**\n```python\nSP500: 25 檔（全是 ETF）\nNASDAQ100: 20 檔（QQQ/SOX 相關）\nSOX30: 23 檔（AMAT/LRCX/MU/NVDA/ASML/KLAC/TSM/INTC/AMD...）\n```\n\n⚠️ **重大問題：SOX30 清單與 vegas_scan.py 完全不一致**\n- `vegas_v1_live.py` SOX30: `AMAT LRCX MU NVDA ASML KLAC TSM INTC AMD QCOM AVGO MRVL MPWR ON MCHP TER ADI SWKS QRVO CRUS LSCC ENTG ALTR`\n- `vegas_scan.py` SOX30: `NVDA AMD INTC AMAT LRCX MU MCHP QRVO QCOM AVGO TXN ADI SWKS CRUS MPWR ON NXPI GFS ENTG KLAC TER ALAB LTHM VSH DIOD AXTI FORM SNPS CDNS ASML`\n\n兩套名單完全不一樣，且 `vegas_v1_live.py` 漏了 `ASML` 在清單前段是另一個版本，`TSM` 在 live 版出現但 scan 版沒有。\n\n**Telegram Token：**\n```\nTG_TOKEN = \"872054…qAiY\"\nTG_CHAT_ID = \"1616824689\"\n```\n這是 Leo 的 bot，**直接 hardcode 在程式碼裡沒有經過 config**。\n\n---\n\n### 🟡 tina_v3_core.py（Pro 分析引擎）\n\n**資料來源優先順序：**\n1. `data/us_history.db`（SQLite，154 檔日線）\n2. yfinance 即時抓取（小時線/日線/週線）\n\n**時間框架：**\n```\n日線（2年）→ 環境過濾\n小時線（30天）→ 進場觸發\n週線（6個月）→ Fib 618 結構\n```\n\n**回測參數（v3.1）：**\n```python\natr_stop_mult: 3.0   # ATR 3x 止損（從 2x 放寬）\ntarget_mult: 2.0     # ATR 2x 目標（從 3x 收緊）\nmax_hold_days: 10    # 持有上限 10 天\nrsi_entry_max: 65    # RSI 必須 < 65 才能進場\n```\n\n**回測結果（2026年3-4月）：**\n| 指標 | 目標 | v3.1 結果 | 狀態 |\n|------|------|---------|------|\n| 勝率 | >55% | **60.0%** | ✅ |\n| 平均報酬 | >2.0% | **0.99%** | ❌ |\n| 最大回撤 | <10% | **-16.47%** | ❌ |\n| Sharpe-like | >0.3 | **0.233** | ⚠️ |\n| 假信號率 | <30% | **46.0%** | ❌ |\n\n→ **系統勝率合格，但報酬/回撤/假信號率都未達標**\n\n---\n\n### 🟢 tina_v3_scoring.py（評分引擎）\n\n**1000 分評分結構：**\n```\n動量分（0-300）\n  1個月動量：120分（≥10%）/ 100分（≥7%）...\n  1週動量：100分（≥8%）/ 80分（≥5%）...\n  3個月動量：80分（≥20%）\n\n趨勢分（0-200）\n  EMA144 > EMA169：+60\n  價格 > EMA144：+40\n  價格 > EMA169：+30\n  EMA144 斜率 ≥0.5%：+30\n  偏離 EMA144 ≤5%：+40\n\nATR 波動分（0-200）\n  ATR% 在 0.5-2.5% 區間：200分（最佳區間）\n\n機構分（0-150）\n  外資淨額 + 信任淨額 各0-75分\n\n結構分（0-150）\n  離 Fib618 支撐 <2%：+80\n  高品質Pivot（≥3組高低點）：+30\n```\n\n**信號閾值：**\n| 分數 | 信號 | 倉位 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 700-1000 | APPROVE | 5% |\n| 500-699 | CAUTION | 2.5% |\n| 350-499 | WATCH | 1% |\n| <350 | REJECT | 0% |\n\n---\n\n### ⚠️ 跨腳本不一致問題\n\n| 項目 | vegas_v1_live.py | vegas_scan.py |\n|------|------------------|--------------|\n| SOX30 名單 | 23檔（AMAT龍頭） | 31檔（ALAB/LTHM/VSH...） |\n| SP500 參與 | ✅（ETF only） | ❌（已移除） |\n| 推播格式 | 完整四階段圖文 | 純終端機表格 |\n| ATR 倍率 | 2.0x | 無（純信號評分） |\n| 主體定位 | Leo（推播bot） | Ray（終端機工具） |\n\n---\n\n### 📌 你問的 MCHP 進場訊號\n\n來自 **`vegas_v1_live.py`**（Leo 的推播腳本），不是 `vegas_scan.py`。\n\n訊號格式完全對應：\n- Step1/2/3/4 核查 → ✅ 來自 `execute_logic()`\n- ATR 2.0x 止損 → ✅ 來自 `vegas_v1_live.py` 的 `ATR_STOP = 2.0`\n- VIX + RSI + 隧道 → ✅ 來自 `execute_logic()` 內的變數\n\n`vegas_scan.py` 只做終端機輸出，沒有推播能力。這是 Leonardo 的系統，**不是 Ray 的**。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3525,"output":1832,"