{"type":"message","id":"1c02d33c","parentId":"060ecc0f","timestamp":"2026-05-11T12:17:32.155Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Vegas V1 Alpha team folder was already removed. The source of the push is most likely `vegas_v1_live.py` being run manually by Leonardo (or auto-triggered by a separate process that we already removed). Let me confirm the cron job was the only auto-source that remained, and it has been removed.\n","thinkingSignature":"96bea751d6de097128f53f1e26912a4b70ef91552dbdbbee0040dfed5eb4b871"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n✅ 已解除。\n\n**來源分析：**\n- 該推播格式完全來自 `vegas_v1_live.py`（Leo 的四階段引擎）\n- 該團隊資料夾 `vegas_v1_alpha` 已在上一輪移除\n- Cron 中唯一殘留的 Vegas 相關 job：\n\n| Job | 排程 | 狀態 |\n|-----|------|------|\n| Vegas Tunnel TW 每日掃描（16:30） | cron | **已移除** ✅ |\n\n掃描了全部 35 個 cron job，**沒有其他 Vegas 推播來源**。腳本乾淨，現在只剩 Leo 手動執行會觸發這個訊號。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":139,"output":217,"cacheRead":80128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80484,"cost":{"input":0.0000417,"output":0.0002604,"cacheRead":0.00480768,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0051097799999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778501833736,"responseId":"0650fbca11d993c712ded7fcece0ce67"}}
