{"type":"message","id":"3e13181b","parentId":"7a3cbaf0","timestamp":"2026-05-11T14:46:05.224Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Jo is sharing the same PDF file again and asking me to read it deeply and apply the concepts to his scripts. Let me first read the full PDF content again, then examine Ray's existing scripts to see how the Tina concepts can be applied.\n","thinkingSignature":"b7bfc6a202135b67e4b7fb1c186321fd77e433ccda951e2361db569e1fa1abfd"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_macwr1yi2whd_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nimport pypdf\nr = pypdf.PdfReader(r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\media\\inbound\\tina_integrated_script_final---d364ed50-6095-4799-98ef-eb17e9c778b0.pdf')\nprint('Pages:', len(r.pages))\nfor i, page in enumerate(r.pages):\n    t = page.extract_text()\n    print(f'=== Page {i+1} ===')\n    print(t)\n\"","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":130296,"output":186,"cacheRead":1344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":131826,"cost":{"input":0.0390888,"output":0.00022319999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00008063999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03939264}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778510748410,"responseId":"06511ea0e82c68dd499a32d3ddc8bafe"}}
{"type":"message","id":"57199076","parentId":"3e13181b","timestamp":"2026-05-11T14:46:05.716Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_macwr1yi2whd_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Pages: 5\r\n=== Page 1 ===\r\nTina 系統：最終整合進化腳本\r\n多源數據融合、自主反思、硬核數學審核、籌碼與美股優化\r\n架構概述： 本系統將 AI 角色從「決策者」轉型為「策略提案者」，核心決策權回歸於嚴格的數學指\r\n標（Sharpe Ratio, MDD）。透過 SQLite 異步紀錄與每週自動重測機制，實現量化交易系統的「數\r\n位韌性」。 \r\n第一部分：數據中心與智慧存儲 (Database)\r\n負責存儲 AI 提案、回測報告與 SOP 版本，解決 JSON 並行寫入損壞與效能問題。\r\nimport sqlite3\r\nimport datetime\r\nfrom contextlib import closing\r\nclass TinaDataCenter:\r\n    def __init__(self, db_path=\"tina_wisdom.db\"):\r\n        self.db_path = db_path\r\n        self._init_db()\r\n    def _init_db(self):\r\n        with closing(sqlite3.connect(self.db_path)) as conn:\r\n            with conn:\r\n                # 智慧紀錄表\r\n                conn.execute(\"\"\"\r\n                    CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS wisdom_logs (\r\n                        id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,\r\n                        timestamp DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,\r\n                        axiom_json TEXT,\r\n                        reflection TEXT,\r\n                        backtest_id INTEGER\r\n                    )\"\"\")\r\n                # 硬核回測報告表\r\n                conn.execute(\"\"\"\r\n                    CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS backtest_reports (\r\n                        id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,\r\n                        sharpe_ratio REAL, max_drawdown REAL, \r\n                        total_return REAL, win_rate REAL,\r\n=== Page 2 ===\r\n                        timestamp DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP\r\n                    )\"\"\")\r\n                # 版本化 SOP\r\n                conn.execute(\"\"\"\r\n                    CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS sop_versions (\r\n                        id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,\r\n                        update_date DATE, content TEXT\r\n                    )\"\"\")\r\n    def log_wisdom(self, axiom_json, reflection, backtest_id=None):\r\n        with closing(sqlite3.connect(self.db_path)) as conn:\r\n            with conn:\r\n                cursor = conn.cursor()\r\n                cursor.execute(\"INSERT INTO wisdom_logs (axiom_json, reflection, \r\nbacktest_id) VALUES (?, ?, ?)\",\r\n                               (axiom_json, reflection, backtest_id))\r\n                return cursor.lastrowid\r\n第二部分：優化回測引擎 (Backtest Engine)\r\n包含摩擦成本 Cfriction、滑價補償及三大法人/美股融合邏輯。\r\nimport pandas as pd\r\nimport numpy as np\r\nimport json\r\nclass TinaEngine:\r\n    def __init__(self, market_type=\"US\"):\r\n        # 台股成本約 0.54%, 美股約 0.15% (視帳戶而定)\r\n        self.costs = 0.0015 if market_type == \"US\" else 0.0054\r\n    def run_backtest(self, df, axiom_str):\r\n        try:\r\n            params = json.loads(axiom_str)\r\n            # 指標計算邏輯 (支援多源融合)\r\n            if params['indicator'] == 'FOREIGN_BUY':\r\n                df['ind'] = df['foreign_net_buy'].rolling(window=params['params']\r\n['window']).sum()\r\n            elif params['indicator'] == 'EMA_CROSS':\r\n                df['fast_ma'] = df['close'].ewm(span=params['params']['fast']).mean()\r\n                df['slow_ma'] = df['close'].ewm(span=params['params']['slow']).mean()\r\n                df['ind'] = df['fast_ma'] - df['slow_ma']\r\n            # 產生訊號與扣除成本\r\n            op = params['entry_condition']['operator']\r\n            threshold = params['entry_condition']['threshold']\r\n=== Page 3 ===\r\n            df['signal'] = (df['ind'] > threshold).astype(int) if op == '>' else \r\n(df['ind'] < threshold).astype(int)\r\n            df['ret'] = df['close'].pct_change()\r\n            df['strat_ret'] = df['signal'].shift(1) * df['ret']\r\n            df['strat_ret'] -= df['signal'].diff().abs() * self.costs\r\n            # 指標把關\r\n            total_ret = (1 + df['strat_ret']).prod() - 1\r\n            sharpe = (df['strat_ret'].mean() / df['strat_ret'].std()) * np.sqrt(252) if \r\ndf['strat_ret'].std() != 0 else 0\r\n            mdd = (df['strat_ret'].cumsum().cummax() - df['strat_ret'].cumsum()).max()\r\n            return {\"sharpe\": sharpe, \"mdd\": mdd, \"total_ret\": total_ret, \"passed\": \r\nsharpe > 1.8 and mdd < 0.2}\r\n        except:\r\n            return {\"passed\": False}\r\n=== Page 4 ===\r\n第三部分：自主進化核心與 NL2Code 驗證 (Evolution Core)\r\n實施 AI 提案 -> 結構化驗證 -> 數學審核 -> 永久存儲的工作流。\r\ndef autonomous_learning_cycle(stock_id, fused_df):\r\n    db = TinaDataCenter()\r\n    engine = TinaEngine(market_type=\"US\")\r\n    # 智慧協議模板\r\n    WISDOM_PROMPT = \"\"\"\r\n    請依據協議輸出 JSON 心法：\r\n    {\r\n        \"strategy_name\": \"STR_NAME\",\r\n        \"indicator\": \"EMA_CROSS | FOREIGN_BUY\",\r\n        \"params\": {\"fast\": 9, \"slow\": 21},\r\n        \"entry_condition\": {\"operator\": \">\", \"threshold\": 0},\r\n        \"stop_loss\": 0.08\r\n    }\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    # 調用 OpenClaw LLM\r\n    raw_proposal = agent_call_llm(WISDOM_PROMPT, fused_df.tail(10)) \r\n    try:\r\n        axiom_json = json.loads(raw_proposal) # 攔截非 JSON 幻覺\r\n        # 數學指標把關 (門檻由開發者硬性設定)\r\n        report = engine.run_backtest(fused_df, raw_proposal)\r\n        if report['passed']:\r\n            with sqlite3.connect(db.db_path) as conn:\r\n                cur = conn.cursor()\r\n                cur.execute(\"\"\"\r\n                    INSERT INTO backtest_reports (sharpe_ratio, max_drawdown, \r\ntotal_return) \r\n                    VALUES (?, ?, ?)\"\"\", (report['sharpe'], report['mdd'], \r\nreport['total_ret']))\r\n                db.log_wisdom(raw_proposal, \"通過硬核回測\", cur.lastrowid)\r\n                print(f\"[Success] 智慧通過驗證，夏普值: {report['sharpe']:.2f}\")\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        print(f\"[Error] 流程攔截: {e}\")\r\n=== Page 5 ===\r\n第四部分：系統健檢總結表\r\n維度 優化措施 目標效果\r\n併發安全 SQLite 事務鎖定 防止多進程寫入損毀\r\n抗幻覺 NL2Code JSON 協議驗證層 攔截 AI 的非格式化自然語言\r\n數學把關 硬核夏普值門檻 (> 1.8) 排除隨機性與運氣成分\r\n成本控制 摩擦成本實體化 (0.15% - 0.54%) 真實模擬市場獲利能力"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":358,"aggregated":"Pages: 5\r\n=== Page 1 ===\r\nTina 系統：最終整合進化腳本\r\n多源數據融合、自主反思、硬核數學審核、籌碼與美股優化\r\n架構概述： 本系統將 AI 角色從「決策者」轉型為「策略提案者」，核心決策權回歸於嚴格的數學指\r\n標（Sharpe Ratio, MDD）。透過 SQLite 異步紀錄與每週自動重測機制，實現量化交易系統的「數\r\n位韌性」。 \r\n第一部分：數據中心與智慧存儲 (Database)\r\n負責存儲 AI 提案、回測報告與 SOP 版本，解決 JSON 並行寫入損壞與效能問題。\r\nimport sqlite3\r\nimport datetime\r\nfrom contextlib import closing\r\nclass TinaDataCenter:\r\n    def __init__(self, db_path=\"tina_wisdom.db\"):\r\n        self.db_path = db_path\r\n        self._init_db()\r\n    def _init_db(self):\r\n        with closing(sqlite3.connect(self.db_path)) as conn:\r\n            with conn:\r\n                # 智慧紀錄表\r\n                conn.execute(\"\"\"\r\n                    CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS wisdom_logs (\r\n                        id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,\r\n                        timestamp DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,\r\n                        axiom_json TEXT,\r\n                        reflection TEXT,\r\n                        backtest_id INTEGER\r\n                    )\"\"\")\r\n                # 硬核回測報告表\r\n                conn.execute(\"\"\"\r\n                    CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS backtest_reports (\r\n                        id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,\r\n                        sharpe_ratio REAL, max_drawdown REAL, \r\n                        total_return REAL, win_rate REAL,\r\n=== Page 2 ===\r\n                        timestamp DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP\r\n                    )\"\"\")\r\n                # 版本化 SOP\r\n                conn.execute(\"\"\"\r\n                    CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS sop_versions (\r\n                        id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,\r\n                        update_date DATE, content TEXT\r\n                    )\"\"\")\r\n    def log_wisdom(self, axiom_json, reflection, backtest_id=None):\r\n        with closing(sqlite3.connect(self.db_path)) as conn:\r\n            with conn:\r\n                cursor = conn.cursor()\r\n                cursor.execute(\"INSERT INTO wisdom_logs (axiom_json, reflection, \r\nbacktest_id) VALUES (?, ?, ?)\",\r\n                               (axiom_json, reflection, backtest_id))\r\n                return cursor.lastrowid\r\n第二部分：優化回測引擎 (Backtest Engine)\r\n包含摩擦成本 Cfriction、滑價補償及三大法人/美股融合邏輯。\r\nimport pandas as pd\r\nimport numpy as np\r\nimport json\r\nclass TinaEngine:\r\n    def __init__(self, market_type=\"US\"):\r\n        # 台股成本約 0.54%, 美股約 0.15% (視帳戶而定)\r\n        self.costs = 0.0015 if market_type == \"US\" else 0.0054\r\n    def run_backtest(self, df, axiom_str):\r\n        try:\r\n            params = json.loads(axiom_str)\r\n            # 指標計算邏輯 (支援多源融合)\r\n            if params['indicator'] == 'FOREIGN_BUY':\r\n                df['ind'] = df['foreign_net_buy'].rolling(window=params['params']\r\n['window']).sum()\r\n            elif params['indicator'] == 'EMA_CROSS':\r\n                df['fast_ma'] = df['close'].ewm(span=params['params']['fast']).mean()\r\n                df['slow_ma'] = df['close'].ewm(span=params['params']['slow']).mean()\r\n                df['ind'] = df['fast_ma'] - df['slow_ma']\r\n            # 產生訊號與扣除成本\r\n            op = params['entry_condition']['operator']\r\n            threshold = params['entry_condition']['threshold']\r\n=== Page 3 ===\r\n            df['signal'] = (df['ind'] > threshold).astype(int) if op == '>' else \r\n(df['ind'] < threshold).astype(int)\r\n            df['ret'] = df['close'].pct_change()\r\n            df['strat_ret'] = df['signal'].shift(1) * df['ret']\r\n            df['strat_ret'] -= df['signal'].diff().abs() * self.costs\r\n            # 指標把關\r\n            total_ret = (1 + df['strat_ret']).prod() - 1\r\n            sharpe = (df['strat_ret'].mean() / df['strat_ret'].std()) * np.sqrt(252) if \r\ndf['strat_ret'].std() != 0 else 0\r\n            mdd = (df['strat_ret'].cumsum().cummax() - df['strat_ret'].cumsum()).max()\r\n            return {\"sharpe\": sharpe, \"mdd\": mdd, \"total_ret\": total_ret, \"passed\": \r\nsharpe > 1.8 and mdd < 0.2}\r\n        except:\r\n            return {\"passed\": False}\r\n=== Page 4 ===\r\n第三部分：自主進化核心與 NL2Code 驗證 (Evolution Core)\r\n實施 AI 提案 -> 結構化驗證 -> 數學審核 -> 永久存儲的工作流。\r\ndef autonomous_learning_cycle(stock_id, fused_df):\r\n    db = TinaDataCenter()\r\n    engine = TinaEngine(market_type=\"US\")\r\n    # 智慧協議模板\r\n    WISDOM_PROMPT = \"\"\"\r\n    請依據協議輸出 JSON 心法：\r\n    {\r\n        \"strategy_name\": \"STR_NAME\",\r\n        \"indicator\": \"EMA_CROSS | FOREIGN_BUY\",\r\n        \"params\": {\"fast\": 9, \"slow\": 21},\r\n        \"entry_condition\": {\"operator\": \">\", \"threshold\": 0},\r\n        \"stop_loss\": 0.08\r\n    }\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    # 調用 OpenClaw LLM\r\n    raw_proposal = agent_call_llm(WISDOM_PROMPT, fused_df.tail(10)) \r\n    try:\r\n        axiom_json = json.loads(raw_proposal) # 攔截非 JSON 幻覺\r\n        # 數學指標把關 (門檻由開發者硬性設定)\r\n        report = engine.run_backtest(fused_df, raw_proposal)\r\n        if report['passed']:\r\n            with sqlite3.connect(db.db_path) as conn:\r\n                cur = conn.cursor()\r\n                cur.execute(\"\"\"\r\n                    INSERT INTO backtest_reports (sharpe_ratio, max_drawdown, \r\ntotal_return) \r\n                    VALUES (?, ?, ?)\"\"\", (report['sharpe'], report['mdd'], \r\nreport['total_ret']))\r\n                db.log_wisdom(raw_proposal, \"通過硬核回測\", cur.lastrowid)\r\n                print(f\"[Success] 智慧通過驗證，夏普值: {report['sharpe']:.2f}\")\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        print(f\"[Error] 流程攔截: {e}\")\r\n=== Page 5 ===\r\n第四部分：系統健檢總結表\r\n維度 優化措施 目標效果\r\n併發安全 SQLite 事務鎖定 防止多進程寫入損毀\r\n抗幻覺 NL2Code JSON 協議驗證層 攔截 AI 的非格式化自然語言\r\n數學把關 硬核夏普值門檻 (> 1.8) 排除隨機性與運氣成分\r\n成本控制 摩擦成本實體化 (0.15% - 0.54%) 真實模擬市場獲利能力","cwd":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778510765716}}
{"type":"message","id":"f9dda285","parentId":"57199076","timestamp":"2026-05-11T14:46:44.841Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the PDF content is identical to the previous one. It's 5 pages, the same Tina integrated script. Now let me provide a thorough review of how to apply these concepts to Ray's scripts.\n\nKey learnings from Tina's document:\n1. SQLite > JSON for concurrent writes\n2. Sharpe Ratio + MDD as gatekeepers\n3. Friction cost modeling (0.15% US / 0.54% TW)\n4. NL2Code JSON validation layer to prevent AI hallucinations\n5. AI as \"strategy proposer\" not \"decision maker\"\n6. Weekly auto-backtest mechanism\n\n\n7. I should now map these principles directly to Ray's actual trading scripts—vegas_scan.py for signal generation, us_momentum.py for momentum analysis, and us_scan_live.py for live scanning—and identify concrete improvements like replacing JSON logs with SQLite, adding Sharpe/MDD backtesting, incorporating friction costs, and potentially building a JSON validation layer to catch hallucinated signals.\n","thinkingSignature":"2f2404ada5a2a84d624f911176f15362f0a0055f9c80bc7bf63a28bd73b126fb"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## Tina 文件應用檢討（針對 Ray 腳本）\n\n---\n\n### 🔍 對照分析\n\n| Tina 原則 | 目前 Ray 腳本 | 差距 |\n|-----------|------------|------|\n| SQLite 持久化 | JSON / CSV 隨手寫 | 🔴 |\n| Sharpe + MDD 把關 | 純 Score 等級制 | 🔴 |\n| 摩擦成本實體化 | 無 | 🔴 |\n| AI 提案→驗證→存儲 workflow | 一次性執行無反饋 | 🔴 |\n| NL2Code JSON 驗證層 | 無 | 🟡 |\n\n---\n\n### 📝 具體應用方案\n\n#### 1️⃣ vegas_scan.py — 加入 Sharpe/MDD 回測層\n\n目前：Score ≥ 3 就輸出，沒有統計意義的把關。\n\n**改進方向：**\n```python\n# 每次 scan 產生的信號\n# → 寫入 SQLite 而非覆蓋 CSV\n# → 計算歷史 Sharpe/MDD\n# → 只推送 Sharpe > 1.5 的信號\n```\n\n#### 2️⃣ us_momentum.py — 加入摩擦成本\n\n目前：純價格變化，沒有交易成本。\n\n**改進方向：**\n```python\nCOST_US = 0.0015  # 0.15% per trade（與 Tina 一致）\n# 每次進出场 扣除 0.15% × 2 = 0.3%\n# 動能策略薄利，成本影響顯著\n```\n\n#### 3️⃣ us_scan_live.py — 升級信號格式\n\n目前：🟢🟡⚪ 簡單分級，沒有統計基礎。\n\n**改進方向：**\n```python\n# 每個信號附加：\n#   sharpe_30d, mdd_30d, win_rate_30d\n# 只對 Sharpe > 1.5 + MDD < 15% 的標的給 BUY 標籤\n```\n\n#### 4️⃣ 全部腳本 — SQLite 取代 CSV\n\n目前：每次執行產生新 CSV，無累積、無版本控制。\n\n**改進方向：**\n```python\n# Ray 的工作日誌：\n#   signals_log（掃描記錄）\n#   positions_log（持倉追蹤）\n#   trades_log（實際交易）\n#   performance_log（每日績效）\n```\n\n---\n\n### ⚠️ Jo 要確認的應用深度\n\n| 選項 | 內容 |\n|------|------|\n| **A. 輕度** | vegas_scan.py 加摩擦成本 + SQLite 日誌 |\n| **B. 中度** | A + 全部腳本加 Sharpe/MDD 把關（不達標不推播） |\n| **C. 重度** | 完整引進 Tina 架構（NL2Code + 回測引擎 + 進化循環） |\n\n要哪個層級？我來實際幫你改寫腳本。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1898,"output":830,"cacheRead":131520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":134248,"cost":{"input":0.0005694,"output":0.000996,"cacheRead":0.0078912,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.009456599999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778510765719,"responseId":"06511eaf77fd06be21d4a87639d992e2"}}
