{"type":"message","id":"2c6e6cc5","parentId":"7e4ac0cc","timestamp":"2026-05-11T15:01:05.981Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All done. Let me give Jo a clean summary.\n","thinkingSignature":"b978c77df0fc4b8c23a32e9b049948f34bf24d16dbcf82f4e20f1fbe05103fe4"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n✅ **完整架構移植完成（Level C）**\n\n---\n\n### 新增/更新的檔案\n\n| 檔案 | 角色 | 大小 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `ray_data_center.py` | SQLite 持久化中心 | 14KB |\n| `ray_engine.py` | 回測引擎 + 數學把關 | 9.7KB |\n| `ray_nl2code.py` | NL2Code 驗證層 | 6.9KB |\n| `ray_evolution.py` | 自主學習循環 | 8.3KB |\n| `vegas_scan.py` | 重寫，接入新架構 | 9.2KB |\n| `us_momentum.py` | 重寫，接入新架構 | 6.2KB |\n| `us_scan_live.py` | 重寫，接入新架構 | 5.3KB |\n| `SOUL.md` | 更新新定位敘述 | — |\n| `ray_wisdom.db` | SQLite資料庫（WAL模式） | 新建 |\n\n---\n\n### 核心改進總結\n\n```\n舊架構：信號 → 輸出（無留存）\n新架構：\n  信號 → SQLite → 數學把關 → 通過才推送\n                   ↓\n           Sharpe>1.5 + MDD<15% + WinRate>45%\n```\n\n**摩擦成本**：0.15% 實體化（每次進出场真實扣除）\n**把關門檻**：Sharpe > 1.5、MDD < 15%、勝率 > 45%\n\n現在可以跑了。要我測試 vegas_scan.py 嗎？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":351,"output":367,"cacheRead":155840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":156558,"cost":{"input":0.0001053,"output":0.00044039999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0093504,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0098961}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778511648055,"responseId":"06512223f8c13bdc4b9ff3cb930aa465"}}
