{"type":"message","id":"0efc5dee","parentId":"78b28a17","timestamp":"2026-05-11T15:42:31.623Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me also create a function/alias for easier access and write the bridge script and modelfile. Also, Ollama needs to be running as a service. Let me first pull the Qwen model and then set up the bridge.\n\nActually, let me first start the Ollama service, then pull the model, and create all the supporting files in parallel.\n","thinkingSignature":"82804f8b8b645c4885861ddc653d31bf5fc17a8f276d565126ca0f877ee380bf"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nOllama 0.23.1 ✅ 已安裝在 `C:\\Users\\USER\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Ollama`\n\n現在啟動服務 + 拉 Qwen 模型 + 建立所有腳本，全部同步進行：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_epo5paeme2gb_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"FROM qwen2.5:1.5b\n\n# 極低隨機性，確保 JSON 輸出穩定\nPARAMETER temperature 0.1\nPARAMETER top_p 0.9\n\n# 利用 32GB RAM 擴展上下文\nPARAMETER num_ctx 8192\n\n# i9-13900H 實用核心數\nPARAMETER num_thread 14\n\nSYSTEM \"\"\"\nYou are the Ray Logic Unit — Tina Architecture Edition.\nOutput MUST be valid JSON. No natural language. No self-introduction.\nSchema: {\"strategy_name\": \"...\", \"indicator\": \"...\", \"params\": {}, \"entry_condition\": {}, \"stop_loss\": 0.0}\n\"\"\"","path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\Tina.Modelfile"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":179,"output":315,"cacheRead":74304,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74798,"cost":{"input":0.0000537,"output":0.00037799999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00445824,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00488994}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778514126081,"responseId":"06512bd50febdf9effb81540d40937e8"}}
