{"type":"message","id":"7afec1de","parentId":"3666b187","timestamp":"2026-05-11T15:50:42.470Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Ollama is running but the version is unclear. The Ollama API endpoint issue is because the OpenAI-compatible endpoint in v0.23.1 might be at a different path. Let me check the actual Ollama API.\n\nThe correct endpoint for Ollama's API is:\n- `http://localhost:11434/api/chat` - for chat completions (POST)\n- `http://localhost:11434/api/generate` - for generate (POST)\n\nThe `/v1/chat/completions` path is for OpenAI compatibility - this is provided by the `llama.cpp` server or an OpenAI proxy, not the native Ollama API. \n\nI need to update the tina_bridge to use Ollama's native `/api/chat` endpoint instead of the OpenAI-compatible path.\n","thinkingSignature":"5031538168d1620102aa19e828cb94da23150339e0a55df67bbef2e7016816f4"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_h6qiq36lrrzb_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$body = @{\"model\"=\"qwen2.5:1.5b\";\"messages\"=@(@{\"role\"=\"user\";\"content\"=\"say hello\"});\"stream\"=$false} | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 3; Invoke-RestMethod -Uri \"http://localhost:11434/api/chat\" -Method POST -ContentType \"application/json\" -Body $body -TimeoutSec 30 2>&1","timeout":"40"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":533,"output":295,"cacheRead":92864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93692,"cost":{"input":0.00015989999999999998,"output":0.000354,"cacheRead":0.00557184,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00608574}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778514622798,"responseId":"06512dc2591818217c0f58f1a2ef74fd"}}
