{"type":"message","id":"9e74dce0","parentId":"e88a7735","timestamp":"2026-05-11T15:58:18.394Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The vegas_scan.py exists at `C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\vegas_scan.py` with 10,221 bytes. It's the file I created earlier today. Jo says it's not on their system - maybe they mean in a different location, or they're testing something. Let me check the AGENTS.md to see what's listed there.\n\nActually, from the directory listing, vegas_scan.py IS present. It's 10,221 bytes and was last modified at 2026/5/11 下午 10:55.\n\nWait - maybe Jo is asking about whether vegas_scan.py should exist at all, given the earlier context about cleaning up old Vegas scripts. \n\nThe earlier conversation involved cleaning up Vegas scripts from Tina's workspace, but the vegas_scan.py in Ray's workspace was explicitly kept since it only scans NASDAQ100 + SOX30 rather than the problematic Taiwan stocks that were removed. The file exists and is functional, so I should confirm that to Jo and explain what it does.\n","thinkingSignature":"cc195a78a00232f9955eea03542008bc499ff36a26d2ecf526396e0b4583a9ec"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nvegas_scan.py **是存在的**。就在你的 Ray 工作區：\n\n```\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\vegas_scan.py  (10,221 bytes, 今天 10:55 更新)\n```\n\n---\n\n### vegas_scan.py 功能說明\n\n這支是我今天重寫的，專門掃描美股：\n\n| 功能 | 說明 |\n|------|------|\n| **NASDAQ100** | 自動從 Wikipedia 抓取完整成分股（~100 檔） |\n| **SOX30** | 31 檔費城半導體強權（NVDA/AMD/ASML/MU...） |\n| **指標** | Vegas Tunnel（EMA144/169/576/676 隧道系統）|\n| **評分** | 0-5 分制， breakout 额外加權 |\n| **數學把關** | Sharpe > 1.5 + MDD < 15% + 勝率 > 45% 才算 BUY |\n| **SQLite** | 所有信號寫入 ray_wisdom.db，持久化追蹤 |\n\n---\n\n### 三支掃描腳本的分工\n\n| 腳本 | 用途 | 特色 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `vegas_scan.py` | Vegas Tunnel 突破掃描 | 隧道邏輯 + 歷史回測把關 |\n| `us_momentum.py` | 動能排名 | 1D/5D/20D 動能 + KDJ + 30日 stat |\n| `us_scan_live.py` | 即時技術掃描 | MA20/MA60 + MACD + RSI + KDJ |\n\n三支都已經整合 Ray 架構（SQLite + Sharpe 把關 + 摩擦成本 0.15%）。\n\n---\n\n要執行哪支掃描？我可以直接跑給你看結果。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":344,"output":606,"cacheRead":97280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98230,"cost":{"input":0.0001032,"output":0.0007272,"cacheRead":0.0058368,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0066672}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778515064883,"responseId":"06512f7b6074adb5183a0bebfb933547"}}
