{"type":"message","id":"de89160a","parentId":"c062f575","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:06:52.572Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_nr018f31rdfq_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Raw: {\"error\": \"Invalid JSON from model\", \"details\": \"```json\r\n{\r\n  \"strategy_name\": \"Tina Architecture Edition\",\r\n  \"indicator\": {\r\n    \"RSI\": 28,\r\n    \"Sharpe_Ratio\": 1.8,\r\n    \"MACD_Cross\": \"Golden\"\r\n  },\r\n  \"params\": {},\r\n  \"entry_condition\": {\r\n    \"Long_Entr\"}\r\npython : Traceback (most recent call last):\r\n位於 線路:1 字元:40\r\n+ cd C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray; python -c \"\r\n+                                        ~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : NotSpecified: (Traceback (most recent call last)::String) [], RemoteException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : NativeCommandError\r\n \r\n  File \"<string>\", line 9, in <module>\r\n  File \"C:\\Users\\USER\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Python\\Python312\\Lib\\json\\__init__.py\", line 346, in loads\r\n    return _default_decoder.decode(s)\r\n           ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\r\n  File \"C:\\Users\\USER\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Python\\Python312\\Lib\\json\\decoder.py\", line 338, in decode\r\n    obj, end = self.raw_decode(s, idx=_w(s, 0).end())\r\n               ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\r\n  File \"C:\\Users\\USER\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Python\\Python312\\Lib\\json\\decoder.py\", line 354, in raw_decode\r\n    obj, end = self.scan_once(s, idx)\r\n               ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\r\njson.decoder.JSONDecodeError: Invalid control character at: line 1 column 57 (char 56)\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":3674,"aggregated":"Raw: {\"error\": \"Invalid JSON from model\", \"details\": \"```json\r\n{\r\n  \"strategy_name\": \"Tina Architecture Edition\",\r\n  \"indicator\": {\r\n    \"RSI\": 28,\r\n    \"Sharpe_Ratio\": 1.8,\r\n    \"MACD_Cross\": \"Gol