{"type":"message","id":"2113f834","parentId":"e2788980","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:11:37.637Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, 7B is downloading. Now let me think about the brain adjustment - dividing labor between local scripts and Qwen models. Let me plan this out properly.\n\nThe division of labor should be:\n\n**Local Python Scripts (no LLM needed):**\n- us_momentum.py: Data fetching (yfinance), momentum calculation, rolling stats (Sharpe/MDD/WinRate)\n- us_scan_live.py: Real-time quotes, MA/RSI/MACD/KDJ calculations\n- ray_data_center.py: SQLite storage\n- ray_engine.py: Backtesting (Sharpe/MDD gates, friction cost)\n\n\n- RayEvolutionCore handles autonomous learning cycles, NL2CodeValidator ensures JSON schema compliance, and tina_bridge.py manages Ollama API calls.\n\n**Qwen 1.5B (fast, local):**\n- Simple strategy proposals based on indicator values\n- Quick signal interpretation and JSON formatting validation\n- High-frequency filtering decisions\n\n**Qwen 7B (deep analysis, local):**\n- Strategy deep reflection and backtest result attribution analysis\n- Market sentiment interpretation from news and complex multi-stock portfolio analysis\n- Advanced JSON schema proposal design\n\nNow I need to identify which scripts require Qwen integration and where it would be most impactful.\n","thinkingSignature":"25f5ee5f631be99fe4cd71e8e33ed95aa9d958fdc6075a829cbea3e520292b74"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n7B 開始下載了。讓我重新整理大腦分工：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vo0cfthr1j5o_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Ray 大腦分工藍圖\n# 本地脚本 vs Qwen 各自的職責邊界\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n層級一：本地 Python（不需要 LLM）\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n負責：客觀計算、數據抓取、數學把關\n\n│ 腳本               │ 職責                              │\n│--------------------│-----------------------------------|\n│ us_momentum.py     │ 1D/5D/20D 動能 + KDJ 計算         │\n│ us_scan_live.py    │ MA20/MA60 + RSI + MACD Hist + KDJ │\n│ ray_data_center.py │ SQLite 持久化（所有數據）           │\n│ ray_engine.py      │ 回測引擎（Sharpe>1.5 / MDD<15%）   │\n│ ray_nl2code.py     │ JSON Schema 驗證（拦截幻覺）        │\n\n摩擦成本：0.15% 美股 / 0.54% 台股\nMath Gate：Sharpe>1.5 + MDD<15% + WinRate>45%\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n層級二：Qwen 1.5B（快速本地推理）\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n負責：即時策略提案、高頻篩選、簡單 JSON 格式化\n\n使用場景：\n  → us_momentum.py 輸出的候選股票，1.5B 快速評估\n  → \"RSI=28, MACD 金叉, Sharpe=1.8\" → 輸出策略 JSON\n  → 每日首次快速掃描（~30 秒內完成）\n  → nl2code.py 格式校驗後的最終確認\n\n速度：CPU 幾秒內回應\n型號：qwen2.5:1.5b（已下載）\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n層級三：Qwen 7B（深度分析）\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n負責：複雜推理、歸因分析、市場情緒、策略進化\n\n使用場景：\n  → RayEvolutionCore 的自主學習（策略提案→回測→迭代）\n  → 回測報告出來後的歸因解讀（為何 Sharpe 高/低？）\n  → 新聞情緒摘要（需要多輪推理）\n  → 投資組合風險評估（多變數複雜判斷）\n  → 進階策略設計（需要突破現有參數框架）\n\n速度：較慢（建議有時間再跑）\n型號：qwen2.5:7b（下載中）\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n分工原則\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n✓ 本地脚本做的：\n  - 數據抓取（yfinance）\n  - 指標計算（RSI/KDJ/MACD/EMA）\n  - 數學把關（Sharpe/MDD/WinRate）\n  - 數據持久化（SQLite）\n  - JSON Schema 驗證\n\n✗ Qwen 做的：\n  - 自然語言 → 結構化策略（NL2Code）\n  - 市場情緒理解\n  - 複雜策略優化建議\n  - 歸因分析（為什麼這個策略有效）\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n實際工作流\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n1. us_momentum.py → 抓到股票數據 → 計算指標\n2. ray_engine.py → 跑 Sharpe/MDD 把關 → 通過的信號進 SQLite\n3. Qwen 1.5B → 把通過的信號轉成策略 JSON → 寫入 signals_log\n4. Qwen 7B → 每日深度複習（進化學習）→ 更新 backtest_reports\n\n這樣每個層級做自己最擅長的事，1.5B 負責快，7B 負責準。","path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\BRAIN_DIVISION.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":139,"output":1104,"cacheRead":109184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110427,"cost":{"input":0.0000417,"output":0.0013248,"cacheRead":0.006551039999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007917539999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778526653303,"responseId":"06515cc0a005d2dc5dbaeb81340dc05a"}}
