{"type":"message","id":"b48c41c7","parentId":"7266225e","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:13:22.114Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Jo wants me to review and revise the brain and memory systems, integrating with Qwen. Let me check what we have and what needs to be updated.\n\nCurrent state:\n- ray_brain.py - model routing (1.5B fast / 7B deep)\n- ray_data_center.py - SQLite persistence\n- ray_engine.py - backtesting engine\n- ray_nl2code.py - JSON validation\n- ray_evolution.py - autonomous learning\n- tina_bridge.py - Ollama bridge\n- BRAIN_DIVISION.md - brain division document\n- Tina.Modelfile - for 1.5B\n- RayDeep.Modelfile - for 7B (already created)\n\n\n- \nI'm verifying the 7B model download is still running, then I'll systematically check what's in memory files and review the existing brain architecture to see what needs fixing or restructuring before integrating Qwen properly.\n","thinkingSignature":"ce0803342b5aea1902463fac98d7abe7c442c5a8ee0955db4162cc2c7e7ec328"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1bfjom72otqf_1","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"log","limit":"5","sessionId":"lucky-ember"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3737,"output":232,"cacheRead":109056,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113025,"cost":{"input":0.0011210999999999999,"output":0.0002784,"cacheRead":0.00654336,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00794286}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778526789583,"responseId":"06515d4bbe0fde0ec4771e25c0bc23a0"}}
