{"type":"message","id":"98b89bd6","parentId":"256d6004","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:13:29.362Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"7B is still downloading. Let me read the existing scripts to understand the current architecture and plan what needs to be updated. Let me look at the key scripts we have.\n","thinkingSignature":"59e3963602974034da625c8a88a28d7dee01d356cb4f225b5bcfad97853638dd"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ljxaq6bnsprj_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\BRAIN_DIVISION.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":423,"output":77,"cacheRead":112768,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113268,"cost":{"input":0.0001269,"output":0.0000924,"cacheRead":0.006766079999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006985379999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778526802229,"responseId":"06515d574e1cf87eb137eb55a44910df"}}
{"type":"message","id":"df19b70b","parentId":"98b89bd6","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:13:29.369Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ljxaq6bnsprj_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Ray 大腦分工藍圖\n# 本地脚本 vs Qwen 各自的職責邊界\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n層級一：本地 Python（不需要 LLM）\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n負責：客觀計算、數據抓取、數學把關\n\n│ 腳本               │ 職責                              │\n│--------------------│-----------------------------------|\n│ us_momentum.py     │ 1D/5D/20D 動能 + KDJ 計算         │\n│ us_scan_live.py    │ MA20/MA60 + RSI + MACD Hist + KDJ │\n│ ray_data_center.py │ SQLite 持久化（所有數據）           │\n│ ray_engine.py      │ 回測引擎（Sharpe>1.5 / MDD<15%）   │\n│ ray_nl2code.py     │ JSON Schema 驗證（拦截幻覺）        │\n\n摩擦成本：0.15% 美股 / 0.54% 台股\nMath Gate：Sharpe>1.5 + MDD<15% + WinRate>45%\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n層級二：Qwen 1.5B（快速本地推理）\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n負責：即時策略提案、高頻篩選、簡單 JSON 格式化\n\n使用場景：\n  → us_momentum.py 輸出的候選股票，1.5B 快速評估\n  → \"RSI=28, MACD 金叉, Sharpe=1.8\" → 輸出策略 JSON\n  → 每日首次快速掃描（~30 秒內完成）\n  → nl2code.py 格式校驗後的最終確認\n\n速度：CPU 幾秒內回應\n型號：qwen2.5:1.5b（已下載）\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n層級三：Qwen 7B（深度分析）\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n負責：複雜推理、歸因分析、市場情緒、策略進化\n\n使用場景：\n  → RayEvolutionCore 的自主學習（策略提案→回測→迭代）\n  → 回測報告出來後的歸因解讀（為何 Sharpe 高/低？）\n  → 新聞情緒摘要（需要多輪推理）\n  → 投資組合風險評估（多變數複雜判斷）\n  → 進階策略設計（需要突破現有參數框架）\n\n速度：較慢（建議有時間再跑）\n型號：qwen2.5:7b（下載中）\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n分工原則\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n✓ 本地脚本做的：\n  - 數據抓取（yfinance）\n  - 指標計算（RSI/KDJ/MACD/EMA）\n  - 數學把關（Sharpe/MDD/WinRate）\n  - 數據持久化（SQLite）\n  - JSON Schema 驗證\n\n✗ Qwen 做的：\n  - 自然語言 → 結構化策略（NL2Code）\n  - 市場情緒理解\n  - 複雜策略優化建議\n  - 歸因分析（為什麼這個策略有效）\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n實際工作流\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n1. us_momentum.py → 抓到股票數據 → 計算指標\n2. ray_engine.py → 跑 Sharpe/MDD 把關 → 通過的信號進 SQLite\n3. Qwen 1.5B → 把通過的信號轉成策略 JSON → 寫入 signals_log\n4. Qwen 7B → 每日深度複習（進化學習）→ 更新 backtest_reports\n\n這樣每個層級做自己最擅長的事，1.5B 負責快，7B 負責準。"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778526809369}}
{"type":"message","id":"d10efa42","parentId":"df19b70b","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:13:37.257Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me read the actual scripts to understand their current state and what needs to be updated to integrate with Qwen.\n","thinkingSignature":"7e190605193973f8c9c2be1597a4471614754476eb6a51bafabfecfc1bc6f902"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0zc5142edb4q_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_data_center.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":874,"output":65,"cacheRead":113152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114091,"cost":{"input":0.0002622,"output":0.000078,"cacheRead":0.006789119999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007129319999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778526809374,"responseId":"06515d5f7343d7b49d21374c21117ee1"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5a1ee180","parentId":"d10efa42","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:13:37.269Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_0zc5142edb4q_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\nRay 數據中心 - Tina 架構移植版\nSQLite 持久化 + 異步事務 + 並發安全\n\nTables:\n  signals_log     - 掃描產生的信號（含 Sharpe/MDD 審核結果）\n  positions_log   - 持倉追蹤\n  trades_log      - 實際成交記錄\n  performance_log - 每日績效（日/週/月）\n  backtest_reports - 回測歷史報告\n  sop_versions    - 版本化 SOP\n\"\"\"\n\nimport sqlite3, json, os\nfrom datetime import datetime, date\nfrom contextlib import closing\nfrom typing import Optional, List, Dict, Any\n\nDB_PATH = os.path.join(os.path.dirname(__file__), \"ray_wisdom.db\")\n\nclass RayDataCenter:\n    def __init__(self, db_path: str = None):\n        self.db_path = db_path or DB_PATH\n        self._init_db()\n\n    def _init_db(self):\n        with closing(sqlite3.connect(self.db_path)) as conn:\n            conn.execute(\"PRAGMA journal_mode=WAL\")   # Write-Ahead Log，並發安全\n            conn.execute(\"PRAGMA synchronous=NORMAL\")   # 效能兼顧安全\n            with conn:\n                # ── 信號日誌（vegas / momentum scan 結果）─────────────────\n                conn.execute(\"\"\"\n                    CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS signals_log (\n                        id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,\n                        timestamp DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,\n                        symbol TEXT NOT NULL,\n                        source TEXT NOT NULL,          -- 'vegas' / 'momentum' / 'live_scan'\n                        score REAL,                    -- 原始評分\n                        sharpe_30d REAL,               -- 30日 Sharpe（由 engine 計算）\n                        mdd_30d REAL,                  -- 30日 MDD\n                        win_rate_30d REAL,            -- 30日勝率\n                        signal_tag TEXT,               -- 'BUY' / 'WATCH' / 'NEUT'\n                        approved BOOLEAN DEFAULT 0,   -- 是否通過數學把關\n                        pushed BOOLEAN DEFAULT 0,     -- 是否已推播\n                        note TEXT\n                    )\"\"\")\n\n                # ── 持倉日誌 ────────────────────────────────────────────\n                conn.execute(\"\"\"\n                    CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS positions_log (\n                        id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,\n                        entry_date DATE NOT NULL,\n                        symbol TEXT NOT NULL,\n                        entry_price REAL NOT NULL,\n                        shares INTEGER,\n                        stop_loss REAL,\n                        target_price REAL,\n                        status TEXT DEFAULT 'open',   -- 'open' / 'closed' / 'stopped'\n                        close_date DATE,\n                        close_price REAL,\n                        close_reason TEXT,\n                        pnl_pct REAL,\n                        rsi_entry REAL,\n                        note TEXT\n                    )\"\"\")\n\n                # ── 成交日誌（實際交易）───────────────────────────────\n                conn.execute(\"\"\"\n                    CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS trades_log (\n                        id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,\n                        trade_date DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,\n                        symbol TEXT NOT NULL,\n                        action TEXT NOT NULL,          -- 'BUY' / 'SELL' / 'ENTRY' / 'EXIT'\n                        price REAL NOT NULL,\n                        shares INTEGER,\n                        amount REAL,\n                        strategy TEXT,                 -- 'vegas' / 'momentum' / 'manual'\n                        pnl_pct REAL,\n                        pnl_abs REAL,\n                        holding_days INTEGER,\n                        close_reason TEXT,\n                        note TEXT\n                    )\"\"\")\n\n                # ── 績效日誌 ───────────────────────────────────────────\n                conn.execute(\"\"\"\n                    CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS performance_log (\n                        id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,\n                        log_date DATE UNIQUE NOT NULL,\n                        portfolio_value REAL,\n                        daily_return_pct REAL,\n                        weekly_return_pct REAL,\n                        monthly_return_pct REAL,\n                        ytd_return_pct REAL,\n                        open_positions INTEGER,\n                        closed_today INTEGER,\n                        total_trades INTEGER,\n                        win_rate_today REAL,\n                        best_trade_pct REAL,\n                        worst_trade_pct REAL,\n                        note TEXT\n                    )\"\"\")\n\n                # ── 回測報告 ───────────────────────────────────────────\n                conn.execute(\"\"\"\n                    CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS backtest_reports (\n                        id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,\n                        timestamp DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,\n                        strategy_name TEXT,\n                        symbol TEXT,\n                        indicator TEXT,\n                        params TEXT,                   -- JSON\n                        sharpe_ratio REAL,\n                        max_drawdown REAL,\n                        total_return REAL,\n                        win_rate REAL,\n                        avg_return REAL,\n                        num_trades INTEGER,\n                        passed BOOLEAN,               -- sharpe > 1.5 and mdd < 0.15\n                        note TEXT\n                    )\"\"\")\n\n                # ── SOP 版本 ─────────────────────────────────────────\n                conn.execute(\"\"\"\n                    CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS sop_versions (\n                        id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,\n                        update_date DATE DEFAULT (date('now')),\n                        version TEXT,\n                        content TEXT,\n                        changelog TEXT\n                    )\"\"\")\n\n    # ── 信號操作 ──────────────────────────────────────────────────\n    def log_signal(self, symbol: str, source: str, score: float,\n                    sharpe: float = None, mdd: float = None, win_rate: float = None,\n                    signal_tag: str = None, note: str = None) -> int:\n        \"\"\"寫入信號，通過數學把關的標記 approved=1\"\"\"\n        approved = 1 if (sharpe is not None and sharpe > 1.5 and mdd is not None and mdd < 0.15) else 0\n        with closing(sqlite3.connect(self.db_path)) as conn:\n            cur = conn.cursor()\n            cur.execute(\"\"\"\n                INSERT INTO signals_log\n                (symbol, source, score, sharpe_30d, mdd_30d, win_rate_30d, signal_tag, approved, note)\n                VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)\"\"\",\n                (symbol, source, score, sharpe, mdd, win_rate, signal_tag, approved, note))\n            return cur.lastrowid\n\n    def get_unpushed_approved_signals(self, source: str = None, limit: int = 20) -> List[Dict]:\n        \"\"\"取尚未推播且通過數學把關的信號\"\"\"\n        sql = \"SELECT * FROM signals_log WHERE approved=1 AND pushed=0\"\n        if source: sql += f\" AND source='{source}'\"\n        sql += \" ORDER BY sharpe_30d DESC LIMIT ?\"\n        with closing(sqlite3.connect(self.db_path)) as conn:\n            conn.row_factory = sqlite3.Row\n            cur = conn.cursor()\n            cur.execute(sql, (limit,))\n            return [dict(r) for r in cur.fetchall()]\n\n    def mark_signals_pushed(self, ids: List[int]):\n        if not ids: return\n        placeholders = \",\".join(\"?\" * len(ids))\n        with closing(sqlite3.connect(self.db_path)) as conn:\n            conn.execute(f\"UPDATE signals_log SET pushed=1 WHERE id IN ({placeholders})\", ids)\n\n    # ── 持倉操作 ──────────────────────────────────────────────────\n    def open_position(self, symbol: str, entry_price: float, shares: int,\n                       stop_loss: float = None, target: float = None,\n                       rsi_entry: float = None, note: str = None) -> int:\n        with closing(sqlite3.connect(self.db_path)) as conn:\n            cur = conn.cursor()\n            cur.execute(\"\"\"\n                INSERT INTO positions_log (entry_date, symbol, entry_price, shares,\n                    stop_loss, target_price, rsi_entry, note)\n                VALUES (date('now'), ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)\"\"\",\n                (symbol, entry_price, shares, stop_loss, target, rsi_entry, note))\n            return cur.lastrowid\n\n    def close_position(self, symbol: str, close_price: float,\n                        reason: str, pnl_pct: float = None) -> int:\n        with closing(sqlite3.connect(self.db_path)) as conn:\n            cur = conn.cursor()\n            cur.execute(\"\"\"\n                UPDATE positions_log SET status='closed', close_date=date('now'),\n                close_price=?, close_reason=?, pnl_pct=?\n                WHERE symbol=? AND status='open'\n                ORDER BY entry_date DESC LIMIT 1\"\"\",\n                (close_price, reason, pnl_pct, symbol))\n            return cur.rowcount\n\n    def get_open_positions(self) -> List[Dict]:\n        with closing(sqlite3.connect(self.db_path)) as conn:\n            conn.row_factory = sqlite3.Row\n            cur = conn.cursor()\n            cur.execute(\"SELECT * FROM positions_log WHERE status='open' ORDER BY entry_date DESC\")\n            return [dict(r) for r in cur.fetchall()]\n\n    def get_position_by_symbol(self, symbol: str) -> Optional[Dict]:\n        with closing(sqlite3.connect(self.db_path)) as conn:\n            conn.row_factory = sqlite3.Row\n            cur = conn.cursor()\n            cur.execute(\"SELECT * FROM positions_log WHERE symbol=? AND status='open' ORDER BY entry_date DESC LIMIT 1\", (symbol,))\n            row = cur.fetchone()\n            return dict(row) if row else None\n\n    # ── 成交操作 ──────────────────────────────────────────────────\n    def log_trade(self, symbol: str, action: str, price: float,\n                   shares: int = None, amount: float = None,\n                   strategy: str = None, pnl_pct: float = None,\n                   holding_days: int = None, close_reason: str = None,\n                   note: str = None) -> int:\n        with closing(sqlite3.connect(self.db_path)) as conn:\n            cur = conn.cursor()\n            cur.execute(\"\"\"\n                INSERT INTO trades_log\n                (symbol, action, price, shares, amount, strategy, pnl_pct, holding_days, close_reason, note)\n                VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)\"\"\",\n                (symbol, action, price, shares, amount, strategy, pnl_pct, holding_days, close_reason, note))\n            return cur.lastrowid\n\n    # ── 績效操作 ──────────────────────────────────────────────────\n    def log_performance(self, portfolio_value: float = None,\n                         daily_return: float = None, open_positions: int = None,\n                         note: str = None) -> int:\n        with closing(sqlite3.connect(self.db_path)) as conn:\n            cur = conn.cursor()\n            # 計算今日 closed 交易\n            cur.execute(\"\"\"SELECT COUNT(*), AVG(pnl_pct) FROM trades_log\n                           WHERE date(trade_date)=date('now') AND action IN ('SELL','EXIT')\"\"\")\n            closed, avg_ret = cur.fetchone()\n\n            cur.execute(\"\"\"\n                INSERT INTO performance_log\n                (log_date, portfolio_value, daily_return_pct, open_positions, closed_today, win_rate_today, note)\n                VALUES (date('now'), ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)\"\"\",\n                (portfolio_value, daily_return, open_positions, closed, avg_ret, note))\n            return cur.lastrowid\n\n    def get_performance_summary(self, days: int = 30) -> Dict:\n        with closing(sqlite3.connect(self.db_path)) as conn:\n            conn.row_factory = sqlite3.Row\n            cur = conn.cursor()\n            cur.execute(f\"\"\"\n                SELECT * FROM performance_log\n                WHERE log_date >= date('now', '-{days} days')\n                ORDER BY log_date ASC\"\"\")\n            rows = [dict(r) for r in cur.fetchall()]\n            if not rows: return {}\n            total_return = sum(r.get('daily_return_pct', 0) or 0 for r in rows)\n            wins = [r for r in rows if r.get('daily_return_pct', 0) > 0]\n            return {\n                'days': len(rows),\n                'total_return_pct': round(total_return * 100, 2),\n                'win_days': len(wins),\n                'win_rate': round(len(wins)/len(rows)*100, 1) if rows else 0,\n                'avg_return': round(total_return/len(rows)*100, 4) if rows else 0,\n            }\n\n    # ── 回測報告 ──────────────────────────────────────────────────\n    def log_backtest(self, strategy_name: str, symbol: str,\n                      indicator: str, params: Dict,\n                      sharpe: float, mdd: float, total_ret: float,\n                      win_rate: float, avg_return: float,\n                      num_trades: int, note: str = None) -> int:\n        passed = 1 if (sharpe > 1.5 and mdd < 0.15) else 0\n        with closing(sqlite3.connect(self.db_path)) as conn:\n            cur = conn.cursor()\n            cur.execute(\"\"\"\n                INSERT INTO backtest_reports\n                (strategy_name, symbol, indicator, params, sharpe_ratio, max_drawdown,\n                 total_return, win_rate, avg_return, num_trades, passed, note)\n                VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)\"\"\",\n                (strategy_name, symbol, indicator, json.dumps(params),\n                 sharpe, mdd, total_ret, win_rate, avg_return, num_trades, passed, note))\n            return cur.lastrowid\n\n    def get_recent_backtests(self, symbol: str = None, days: int = 30) -> List[Dict]:\n        sql = \"SELECT * FROM backtest_reports WHERE timestamp >= datetime('now', ?)\"\n        params = [f'-{days} days']\n        if symbol: sql += f\" AND symbol='{symbol}'\"\n        sql += \" ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 50\"\n        with closing(sqlite3.connect(self.db_path)) as conn:\n            conn.row_factory = sqlite3.Row\n            cur = conn.cursor()\n            cur.execute(sql, params)\n            return [dict(r) for r in cur.fetchall()]\n\n    def get_approved_backtests(self, limit: int = 20) -> List[Dict]:\n        with closing(sqlite3.connect(self.db_path)) as conn:\n            conn.row_factory = sqlite3.Row\n            cur = conn.cursor()\n            cur.execute(\"\"\"\n                SELECT * FROM backtest_reports\n                WHERE passed=1\n                ORDER BY sharpe_ratio DESC LIMIT ?\"\"\", (limit,))\n            return [dict(r) for r in cur.fetchall()]\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    db = RayDataCenter()\n    print(f\"[RayDataCenter] DB initialized: {db.db_path}\")\n    print(f\"[RayDataCenter] Tables: signals_log, positions_log, trades_log, performance_log, backtest_reports, sop_versions\")"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778526817269}}
{"type":"message","id":"7e61755c","parentId":"5a1ee180","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:13:48.077Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me review the other key files and then redesign the system to properly integrate Qwen into the workflow. The key issues I see:\n\n1. `ray_evolution.py` references `log_wisdom` which doesn't exist in `ray_data_center.py`\n2. The scripts don't actually USE Qwen - they compute signals locally but don't feed them to the model\n3. `ray_data_center.py` needs `log_wisdom` for the evolution cycle\n4. The scan scripts need to be unified with a proper brain-driven workflow\n\nLet me plan the fixes:\n1. Add `log_wisdom` table + method to `ray_data_center.py`\n2. Fix `ray_evolution.py` to use `log_wisdom` and work correctly\n\n\n3. Create a unified `ray_scanner.py` that replaces both momentum and live scan and integrates Qwen for idea generation\n4. Create `ray_memory.py` as a proper Qwen-powered memory/context system\n5. Update `ray_engine.py` to be more robust\n\nI'll work through these fixes systematically.\n","thinkingSignature":"8c46ff897649edb1b4664a10353a369664e7695dafc6604a9ea5f2a81969a8a3"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好，全面檢討。讓我看一下所有腳本：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_islxuiam4kav_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_evolution.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3243,"output":274,"cacheRead":113984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117501,"cost":{"input":0.0009729,"output":0.00032879999999999997,"cacheRead":0.006839039999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.008140739999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778526817274,"responseId":"06515d638ea332ff80c65e9f7fb3096d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"03720394","parentId":"7e61755c","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:13:48.085Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_islxuiam4kav_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\nRay 進化核心 - Tina autonomous_learning_cycle 移植版\nAI 提案 → NL2Code 驗證 → 數學審核 → SQLite 永久存儲\n\n工作流：\n  1. LLM 根據市場數據生成策略提案（自然語言）\n  2. NL2Code 層拦截，強制轉為結構化 JSON\n  3. 回測引擎跑 Sharpe/MDD 把關\n  4. 通過 → 寫入 backtest_reports + signals_log\n     失敗 → 記錄失敗原因（供下次學習）\n\"\"\"\n\nimport json\nimport yfinance as yf\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom typing import Dict, Optional, List, Tuple\n\nfrom ray_data_center import RayDataCenter\nfrom ray_engine import RayEngine\nfrom ray_nl2code import NL2CodeValidator, sanitize_llm_output\n\n\n# ── 智慧協議模板（給 LLM 看的格式說明）────────────────────────────────\nWISDOM_PROMPT_TEMPLATE = \"\"\"你是 Ray 的策略進化引擎。\n根據以下市場數據，生成一個交易策略提案（JSON 格式）。\n\n約束：\n- strategy_name: 大寫 UPPER_SNAKE_CASE，3-30字\n- indicator: EMA_CROSS | VEGAS_TUNNEL | FOREIGN_BUY | MOMENTUM | KDJ_CROSS | RSI_THRESHOLD\n- params: 具體數字（不要用變量）\n- entry_condition: operator 是 > < >= <= CROSS_ABOVE CROSS_BELOW\n- stop_loss: 0.01-0.50（小數）\n- max_hold_days: 1-60\n\n輸出格式（只輸出 JSON，不要其他文字）：\n{\n    \"strategy_name\": \"EMA_CROSS_9_21\",\n    \"indicator\": \"EMA_CROSS\",\n    \"params\": {\"fast\": 9, \"slow\": 21},\n    \"entry_condition\": {\"operator\": \"CROSS_ABOVE\", \"threshold\": 0},\n    \"stop_loss\": 0.08,\n    \"max_hold_days\": 10\n}\n\n市場數據摘要：\n{snippet}\n\"\"\"\n\n\nclass RayEvolutionCore:\n    \"\"\"\n    自主學習循環：提案 → 驗證 → 回測 → 存儲\n    \"\"\"\n\n    def __init__(self, db_path: str = None):\n        self.db     = RayDataCenter(db_path)\n        self.engine = RayEngine(market_type=\"US\", db_path=db_path)\n        self.validator = NL2CodeValidator()\n        self.learned_count   = 0\n        self.rejected_count  = 0\n\n    # ── 核心：自動學習循環（單檔）──────────────────────────────────\n    def autonomous_learning_cycle(self, symbol: str,\n                                   lookback_days: int = 730,\n                                   min_shappe: float = 1.5,\n                                   max_mdd: float = 0.15) -> Dict:\n        \"\"\"\n        對單一標的執行完整的自主學習循環\n\n        步驟：\n        1. 抓取歷史數據\n        2. 嘗試多個候選策略（網格搜索）\n        3. 每個策略經過 NL2Code + 回測把關\n        4. 最好且通過的把關策略寫入 DB\n\n        返回：{status, best_strategy, sharpe, mdd, ...}\n        \"\"\"\n        print(f\"[RayEvolution] Learning cycle for {symbol}...\")\n\n        # ── 抓數據 ───────────────────────────────────────────────\n        try:\n            df = yf.Ticker(symbol).history(period=f\"{lookback_days}d\",\n                                           interval=\"1d\", auto_adjust=True)\n            if df is None or len(df) < 200:\n                return {\"status\": \"error\", \"reason\": \"insufficient data\"}\n        except Exception as e:\n            return {\"status\": \"error\", \"reason\": str(e)}\n\n        # ── 網格候選參數（Ray 擅長的策略）──────────────────────────\n        candidates = []\n\n        # Vegas Tunnel\n        for ema_fast in [144, 169]:\n            for ema_slow in [576, 676]:\n                if ema_fast >= ema_slow: continue\n                candidates.append({\n                    \"strategy_name\": f\"VEGAS_TUNNEL_{ema_fast}_{ema_slow}\",\n                    \"indicator\": \"VEGAS_TUNNEL\",\n                    \"params\": {\"fast\": ema_fast, \"slow\": ema_slow},\n                    \"entry_condition\": {\"operator\": \"CROSS_ABOVE\", \"threshold\": 0},\n                    \"stop_loss\": 0.08,\n                    \"max_hold_days\": 10,\n                })\n\n        # EMA Cross\n        for fast, slow in [(9, 21), (12, 26), (20, 60), (50, 200)]:\n            candidates.append({\n                \"strategy_name\": f\"EMA_CROSS_{fast}_{slow}\",\n                \"indicator\": \"EMA_CROSS\",\n                \"params\": {\"fast\": fast, \"slow\": slow},\n                \"entry_condition\": {\"operator\": \"CROSS_ABOVE\", \"threshold\": 0},\n                \"stop_loss\": 0.08,\n                \"max_hold_days\": 15,\n            })\n\n        # Momentum\n        for window in [5, 10, 20, 60]:\n            candidates.append({\n                \"strategy_name\": f\"MOMENTUM_{window}\",\n                \"indicator\": \"MOMENTUM\",\n                \"params\": {\"window\": window},\n                \"entry_condition\": {\"operator\": \">\", \"threshold\": 0.02},\n                \"stop_loss\": 0.10,\n                \"max_hold_days\": 20,\n            })\n\n        # ── NL2Code 驗證 + 回測把關 ─────────────────────────────────\n        passed_strategies = []\n        for axiom in candidates:\n            # NL2Code 驗證\n            is_valid, parsed, errors = self.validator.validate(axiom)\n            if not is_valid:\n                continue  # 格式不合，自動跳過\n\n            # 回測把關\n            report = self.engine.run_backtest(df, axiom)\n            if report[\"passed\"]:\n                passed_strategies.append({**report, \"axiom\": axiom})\n                backtest_id = self.db.log_backtest(\n                    strategy_name = axiom[\"strategy_name\"],\n                    symbol        = symbol,\n                    indicator     = axiom[\"indicator\"],\n                    params        = axiom[\"params\"],\n                    sharpe        = report[\"sharpe\"],\n                    mdd           = report[\"mdd\"],\n                    total_ret     = report[\"total_ret\"],\n                    win_rate      = report[\"win_rate\"],\n                    avg_return    = report[\"avg_return\"],\n                    num_trades    = report[\"num_trades\"],\n                    note          = f\"auto_learned | cost={report.get('cost_pct',0.15)}%\",\n                )\n                self.db.log_wisdom(\n                    axiom_json = json.dumps(axiom),\n                    reflection = f\"SHARP={report['sharpe']:.2f} MDD={report['mdd']:.2%} WIN={report['win_rate']:.1%}\",\n                    backtest_id = backtest_id,\n                )\n\n        # ── 選最佳策略 ─────────────────────────────────────────────\n        if passed_strategies:\n            best = sorted(passed_strategies, key=lambda x: -x[\"sharpe\"])[0]\n            self.learned_count += 1\n            print(f\"[RayEvolution] ✅ {symbol}: {len(passed_strategies)} passed, best Sharpe={best['sharpe']:.2f}\")\n            return {\n                \"status\":         \"success\",\n                \"symbol\":         symbol,\n                \"best_strategy\":  best[\"axiom\"][\"strategy_name\"],\n                \"indicator\":       best[\"axiom\"][\"indicator\"],\n                \"sharpe\":         best[\"sharpe\"],\n                \"mdd\":            best[\"mdd\"],\n                \"total_ret\":      best[\"total_ret\"],\n                \"win_rate\":       best[\"win_rate\"],\n                \"num_trades\":     best[\"num_trades\"],\n                \"passed_count\":   len(passed_strategies),\n            }\n        else:\n            self.rejected_count += 1\n            # 記錄失敗\n            self.db.log_wisdom(\n                axiom_json = json.dumps({\"symbol\": symbol, \"attempted\": len(candidates)}),\n                reflection = f\"No strategy passed (tried {len(candidates)})\",\n            )\n            print(f\"[RayEvolution] ❌ {symbol}: all {len(candidates)} strategies rejected\")\n            return {\n                \"status\":   \"rejected\",\n                \"symbol\":   symbol,\n                \"attempted\": len(candidates),\n            }\n\n    # ── 批量學習（多檔）────────────────────────────────────────────\n    def batch_learning(self, symbols: List[str], lookback_days: int = 730) -> List[Dict]:\n        results = []\n        for sym in symbols:\n            r = self.autonomous_learning_cycle(sym, lookback_days)\n            results.append(r)\n        return results\n\n    # ── 讀取已知的好策略（通過把關的）─────────────────────────────\n    def get_approved_strategies(self, limit: int = 20) -> List[Dict]:\n        return self.db.get_approved_backtests(limit=limit)\n\n    # ── 讀取近期學習摘要 ─────────────────────────────────────────\n    def get_learning_stats(self) -> Dict:\n        recent = self.db.get_recent_backtests(days=7)\n        approved = [r for r in recent if r.get(\"passed\")]\n        return {\n            \"total_learned\":   self.learned_count,\n            \"total_rejected\":  self.rejected_count,\n            \"recent_backtests\": len(recent),\n            \"recent_approved\":  len(approved),\n            \"avg_sharpe\":      round(sum(r[\"sharpe_ratio\"] for r in approved) / max(len(approved), 1), 2),\n            \"avg_mdd\":         round(sum(r[\"max_drawdown\"] for r in approved) / max(len(approved), 1), 4),\n        }\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    core = RayEvolutionCore()\n    result = core.autonomous_learning_cycle(\"NVDA\", lookback_days=365)\n    print(f\"Result: {result}\")"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778526828085}}
{"type":"message","id":"d6b1e81c","parentId":"03720394","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:13:56.634Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see there's a call to `self.db.log_wisdom()` in `ray_evolution.py` but that method doesn't exist in `ray_data_center.py`. I need to add it. Also I need to check `ray_engine.py` for the same missing method.\n\nAlso, `ray_evolution.py` imports `sanitize_llm_output` but that function isn't exported from `ray_nl2code.py`. \n\nAlso, the evolution core doesn't use Qwen at all - it only uses fixed candidate strategies. The whole point of \"evolution\" should be to use Qwen to propose NEW strategies based on market data, not just grid search through fixed candidates.\n\n\nSo I need to add the `log_wisdom()` method to the data center, fix the import of `sanitize_llm_output` from the NL2Code module, and most importantly, integrate Qwen into the evolution loop so it can dynamically propose new strategies instead of relying on a static grid.\n","thinkingSignature":"558744964e14888ef60989583bec9254be37797bd3cc848c687242f31c4a6e8c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zp305p7xih7m_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_nl2code.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2304,"output":240,"cacheRead":117184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119728,"cost":{"input":0.0006912,"output":0.000288,"cacheRead":0.00703104,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00801024}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778526828090,"responseId":"06515d6d9a33de6d82eeac8619a54e17"}}
{"type":"message","id":"81aeb431","parentId":"d6b1e81c","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:13:56.646Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_zp305p7xih7m_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\nRay NL2Code 驗證層 — Tina 架構移植版\nJSON Schema 拦截 AI 幻覺，確保策略提案為結構化格式\n\"\"\"\n\nimport json\nimport re\nfrom typing import Dict, List, Optional, Tuple\n\n# ── 嚴格的策略協議 Schema ───────────────────────────────────────────\nAXIOM_SCHEMA = {\n    \"type\": \"object\",\n    \"required\": [\"strategy_name\", \"indicator\", \"params\", \"entry_condition\"],\n    \"properties\": {\n        \"strategy_name\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"pattern\": \"^[A-Z][A-Z0-9_]{2,30}$\"  # 大寫字母+數字+底線\n        },\n        \"indicator\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\"EMA_CROSS\", \"VEGAS_TUNNEL\", \"FOREIGN_BUY\", \"MOMENTUM\",\n                     \"KDJ_CROSS\", \"RSI_THRESHOLD\", \"MACD_CROSS\", \"MA_BREAKOUT\"]\n        },\n        \"params\": {\n            \"type\": \"object\",\n            \"properties\": {\n                \"fast\":   {\"type\": \"integer\", \"minimum\": 2, \"maximum\": 200},\n                \"slow\":   {\"type\": \"integer\", \"minimum\": 5, \"maximum\": 500},\n                \"window\": {\"type\": \"integer\", \"minimum\": 2, \"maximum\": 300},\n                \"rsi_period\":  {\"type\": \"integer\", \"minimum\": 2, \"maximum\": 50},\n                \"rsi_buy\":     {\"type\": \"number\",  \"minimum\": 10, \"maximum\": 60},\n                \"rsi_sell\":    {\"type\": \"number\",  \"minimum\": 50, \"maximum\": 95},\n                \"atr_period\":  {\"type\": \"integer\", \"minimum\": 5, \"maximum\": 50},\n                \"stop_loss_pct\": {\"type\": \"number\", \"minimum\": 0.01, \"maximum\": 0.30},\n                \"target_pct\":    {\"type\": \"number\", \"minimum\": 0.01, \"maximum\": 1.00},\n            }\n        },\n        \"entry_condition\": {\n            \"type\": \"object\",\n            \"required\": [\"operator\", \"threshold\"],\n            \"properties\": {\n                \"operator\":  {\"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\">\", \"<\", \">=\", \"<=\", \"CROSS_ABOVE\", \"CROSS_BELOW\"]},\n                \"threshold\": {\"type\": \"number\"}\n            }\n        },\n        \"stop_loss\": {\"type\": \"number\", \"minimum\": 0.01, \"maximum\": 0.50},\n        \"target\":    {\"type\": \"number\", \"minimum\": 0.01, \"maximum\": 2.00},\n        \"max_hold_days\": {\"type\": \"integer\", \"minimum\": 1, \"maximum\": 60}\n    }\n}\n\n\nclass NL2CodeValidator:\n    \"\"\"\n    职责：拦截 AI 自然語言輸出中的「幻覺」，確保所有策略都是合法的結構化 JSON\n    仿 Tina 的 NL2Code 驗證層\n    \"\"\"\n\n    def __init__(self, schema: Dict = None):\n        self.schema = schema or AXIOM_SCHEMA\n        self.errors: List[str] = []\n\n    def validate(self, axiom_json: str) -> Tuple[bool, Optional[Dict], List[str]]:\n        \"\"\"\n        輸入：可能是 JSON 字串或已經是 dict\n        輸出：(is_valid, parsed_axiom, errors)\n        \"\"\"\n        self.errors = []\n\n        # ── Step 1：嘗試解析 JSON ────────────────────────────────\n        if isinstance(axiom_json, str):\n            try:\n                axiom = json.loads(axiom_json)\n            except json.JSONDecodeError as e:\n                self.errors.append(f\"JSON parse failed: {e}\")\n                return False, None, self.errors\n        elif isinstance(axiom_json, dict):\n            axiom = axiom_json\n        else:\n            self.errors.append(f\"Unknown type: {type(axiom_json)}\")\n            return False, None, self.errors\n\n        # ── Step 2：檢查必要欄位 ─────────────────────────────────\n        for field in self.schema.get(\"required\", []):\n            if field not in axiom:\n                self.errors.append(f\"Missing required field: {field}\")\n\n        # ── Step 3：檢查 strategy_name 格式 ──────────────────────\n        name = axiom.get(\"strategy_name\", \"\")\n        if not re.match(r\"^[A-Z][A-Z0-9_]{2,30}$\", name):\n            self.errors.append(f\"Invalid strategy_name '{name}': must be UPPER_SNAKE_CASE 3-30 chars\")\n\n        # ── Step 4：檢查 indicator 合法值 ────────────────────────\n        valid_indicators = AXIOM_SCHEMA[\"properties\"][\"indicator\"][\"enum\"]\n        ind = axiom.get(\"indicator\")\n        if ind and ind not in valid_indicators:\n            self.errors.append(f\"Unknown indicator '{ind}': must be one of {valid_indicators}\")\n\n        # ── Step 5：檢查 params 範圍 ─────────────────────────────\n        params = axiom.get(\"params\", {})\n        param_specs = AXIOM_SCHEMA[\"properties\"][\"params\"][\"properties\"]\n        for key, spec in param_specs.items():\n            if key in params:\n                val = params[key]\n                if spec[\"type\"] == \"integer\":\n                    if not isinstance(val, int):\n                        self.errors.append(f\"params.{key} must be int, got {type(val).__name__}\")\n                    elif \"minimum\" in spec and val < spec[\"minimum\"]:\n                        self.errors.append(f\"params.{key}={val} < minimum {spec['minimum']}\")\n                    elif \"maximum\" in spec and val > spec[\"maximum\"]:\n                        self.errors.append(f\"params.{key}={val} > maximum {spec['maximum']}\")\n\n        # ── Step 6：檢查 entry_condition ──────────────────────────\n        ec = axiom.get(\"entry_condition\", {})\n        for field in [\"operator\", \"threshold\"]:\n            if field not in ec:\n                self.errors.append(f\"entry_condition missing '{field}'\")\n\n        # ── Step 7：檢查 stop_loss / target 範圍 ─────────────────\n        if \"stop_loss\" in axiom:\n            sl = axiom[\"stop_loss\"]\n            if not (0.01 <= sl <= 0.50):\n                self.errors.append(f\"stop_loss={sl} must be between 0.01-0.50\")\n\n        if \"target\" in axiom:\n            tgt = axiom[\"target\"]\n            if not (0.01 <= tgt <= 2.00):\n                self.errors.append(f\"target={tgt} must be between 0.01-2.00\")\n\n        is_valid = len(self.errors) == 0\n        return is_valid, axiom if is_valid else None, self.errors\n\n    def validate_batch(self, axiom_list: List[str]) -> List[Tuple[bool, Optional[Dict], List[str]]]:\n        \"\"\"批量驗證多個策略提案\"\"\"\n        return [self.validate(a) for a in axiom_list]\n\n\ndef sanitize_llm_output(raw_output: str) -> str:\n    \"\"\"\n    在 JSON 解析前，先尝试清理 LLM 输常见的格式問題\n    - 移除 markdown code block\n    - 移除解释性文字\n    - 只保留第一个 { ... } JSON block\n    \"\"\"\n    # 移除 ```json ... ``` 或 ``` ... ```\n    pattern = r\"```(?:json)?\\s*([\\s\\S]*?)```\"\n    matches = re.findall(pattern, raw_output)\n    for block in matches:\n        try:\n            json.loads(block)\n            return block\n        except:\n            pass\n\n    # 找第一個完整的 {...} JSON 區塊\n    start = raw_output.find(\"{\")\n    end   = raw_output.rfind(\"}\") + 1\n    if start >= 0 and end > start:\n        candidate = raw_output[start:end]\n        try:\n            json.loads(candidate)\n            return candidate\n        except:\n            pass\n\n    return raw_output  # fallback\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    # 測試\n    v = NL2CodeValidator()\n\n    good = '{\"strategy_name\":\"EMA_CROSS_12_26\",\"indicator\":\"EMA_CROSS\",\"params\":{\"fast\":12,\"slow\":26},\"entry_condition\":{\"operator\":\">\",\"threshold\":0},\"stop_loss\":0.08}'\n    ok, ax, errs = v.validate(good)\n    print(f\"Good: valid={ok}, errors={errs}\")\n\n    bad = '{\"strategy_name\":\"ema cross bad\",\"indicator\":\"BOGUS\",\"params\":{\"fast\":9999},\"entry_condition\":{}}'\n    ok2, ax2, errs2 = v.validate(bad)\n    print(f\"Bad: valid={ok2}, errors={errs2}\")"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778526836646}}
