{"type":"message","id":"b06cfa1e","parentId":"0a67cf21","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:14:12.574Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The memory directory is empty. Now let me build the updated architecture. Here's my plan:\n\n**Issues found:**\n1. `log_wisdom` referenced in `ray_evolution.py` but doesn't exist in `ray_data_center.py`\n2. `ray_data_center.py` missing `log_wisdom` table and method\n3. `ray_evolution.py` tries to call `sanitize_llm_output` but it's in `ray_nl2code.py` - need to check import\n4. `ray_brain.py` is new and well-structured\n5. Memory system is empty - needs to be set up\n\n\n6. I need to add the missing `log_wisdom` method to `ray_data_center.py` with its associated table and queries, fix the import in `ray_evolution.py` to properly reference `sanitize_llm_output` from `ray_nl2code.py`, and create an actual memory system that persists Ray's knowledge and learning progress.\n","thinkingSignature":"74f42fc2c139516e5c627fefcef347cf6a2b019519708b3b88dc6ca785959533"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bjlj52ebvzvk_1","name":"update_plan","arguments":{"plan":"[{\"status\": \"in_progress\", \"step\": \"修正 ray_data_center.py — 新增 log_wisdom 缺失方法\"}, {\"status\": \"pending\", \"step\": \"修正 ray_evolution.py — 修正 log_wisdom + sanitize 調用\"}, {\"status\": \"pending\", \"step\": \"升級 ray_brain.py — 整合 1.5B + 7B 路由 + 對接本地腳本\"}, {\"status\": \"pending\", \"step\": \"建立 memory 目錄 — 讓 Ray 有長期記憶\"}, {\"status\": \"pending\", \"step\": \"更新 AGENTS.md — 同步新架構\"}, {\"status\": \"pending\", \"step\": \"等 7B 下載完成後建立 ray-deep-v1 模型\"}]"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":114,"output":388,"cacheRead":121408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121910,"cost":{"input":0.0000342,"output":0.0004656,"cacheRead":0.007284479999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007784279999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778526840119,"responseId":"06515d79469a9837a08b64a8293104b8"}}
