{"type":"message","id":"f5a89837","parentId":"da69257e","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:54:00.787Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"檢討這個推播來源並取消\nReply target of current user message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Ray\",\n  \"body\": \"🚀 Vegas V1 Alpha 進場訊號\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n📌 標的: ENTG\\n💰 現價: $149.10\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n【四階段核查】\\n✅ Step1 日線環境：多頭 + 隧道斜率向上\\n✅ Step2 Fib618 共振區：$147.93 落在隧道區間\\n✅ Step3 動能觸發：J 線低位(<20)勾頭 + 站上 EMA12 + MACD 轉強\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n【風控】\\n🛡️ 動態止損: $136.16 (ATR×2.0)\\n⚠️ 預警線: $137.38 (ATR×1.5)\\n🎯 獲利目標: $154.79 (Fib 1.618 擴展)\\n📈 保本觸發價: $152.21 (1.272×ATR)\\n⏱ 持有上限: 10 天\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\nVIX:18.1 | RSI:57.0 | 隧道:[141.0-142.6]\"\n}\n```"}],"timestamp":1778501736501}}
