{"type":"message","id":"78d94f40","parentId":"479653f4","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:54:00.787Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"RSI is 69 and price is above both MA20 and MA60. So we should have:\n- above_ma20 = True (+1)\n- above_ma60 = True (+1)\n- macd_bull = True (macd_hist > 0) (+1)\n- kdj_bull = j0 > j1 and 10 < j0 < 85\n\nJ was showing 202 which is > 85, so kdj_bull fails.\n\nScore = 3 -> BUY signal. But the output said \"No BUY signals\". Something must be going wrong in the loop logic when running the script. Let me look at the script and try running it with more debug output.\n","thinkingSignature":"74b8c4e4d8f6416f5e043c827511b186c276927ab9d5d16eea611dd812dc4c2a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pead2de4du8d_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\us_scan_live.py 2>&1","timeout":"120"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":295,"output":201,"cacheRead":101952,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102448,"cost":{"input":0.0000885,"output":0.00024119999999999998,"cacheRead":0.006117119999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006446819999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778507332089,"responseId":"06511145d038e1a2ad814a1cfe3bfbec"}}
