re buying everything connected to AI and data centers across multiple levels of the supply chain.\n\nNow I'm structuring this as a comprehensive 7-layer analysis framework—starting with the physical infrastructure like power and cooling, moving through the hardware layer, then accelerators and chips, cloud infrastructure, and continuing upward through the full stack.\n\nSince this is a concept analysis rather than specific stock recommendations, I'll pull current market data for each layer to show how the AI infrastructure trade is playing out.\n","thinkingSignature":"a8aab5de4e105b916183879dfff5ecd8ceba622272cd5ede7a2768ab3e317da9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tqxpk5s5oumu_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\us_momentum.py 2>/dev/null","timeout":120,"yieldMs":110000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":112341,"output":543,"cacheRead":512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113396,"cost":{"input":0.0337023,"output":0.0006516,"cacheRead":0.00003072,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03438462}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778508803540,"responseId":"06511706c9a4dcdb2574fe18f37bd3c8"}}
