{"type":"compaction","id":"9e331259","parentId":"600076e1","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:54:00.788Z","summary":"\n\n## Goal\n- Clean up all Vegas V1 Alpha scripts and Leo's four-stage engine (fully completed in prior turns)\n- Adopt Tina's full architecture (NL2Code validation + backtesting engine + evolution cycles) into Ray's existing US stock scripts (us_scan_live.py, us_momentum.py, vegas_scan.py)\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Only NASDAQ100 + SOX30 for stock scanning (TW/SP500 removed from vegas_scan.py)\n- Full adoption of Tina's framework (User chose option C — \"heavy\")\n- Scripts must run in Ray's agent workspace (`C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\`)\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] vegas_scan.py modified to scan only NASDAQ100 + SOX30 (removed TWSE/SP500)\n- [x] vegas_scan.py 4 bug fixes applied (RSI NaN guard, sleep 0.15s, failed ticker tracking, dict(res).items() → for r in res)\n- [x] All Vegas scripts removed from workspace: `workspace/scripts/` (12 files), `workspace/vegas_hourly_check.py`, `Tina_Quant_System/scripts/vegas_daily_scan.py`, `Tina_Quant_System/teams/tina_v3_alpha/vegas_dashboard.py`, `Tina_Quant_System/teams/vegas_v1_alpha/` (entire folder), `Tina_Quant_System/data/vegas_tunnel_scan.json`, `agents/ray/vegas_scan.py`, `agents/ray/vegas_streamlit.py`, `agents/ray/vegas_results_20260511_185952.csv`\n- [x] Vegas Tunnel TW cron job removed (`id: 9dcfa4d6-6308-4bb6-9f26-a7ed50f1d47b`)\n- [x] us_scan_live.py created — live US tech quotes with MACD/KDJ/MA indicators\n- [x] us_momentum.py created — US stock momentum analysis (5D/20D rankings)\n- [x] Tina PDF `tina_integrated_script_final.pdf` (5 pages) analyzed and reviewed\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Heavy adoption of Tina's architecture into Ray's scripts (option C selected by Jo)\n\n### Blocked\n- (none)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **vegas_scan.py scope**: Only NASDAQ100 (from Wikipedia) + SOX30 (31 stocks hardcoded), removed S&P500 and TWSE entirely\n- **vegas_v1_live.py push source confirmed as external**: Telegram bot token `872054…qAiY` hardcoded in Leo's script; runs outside OpenClaw; script deleted from workspace but may still run on Leo's local machine\n- **User chose option C (heavy)**: Full introduction of Tina architecture — NL2Code + backtesting engine + evolution cycles + SQLite persistence + Sharpe/MDD gatekeepers + friction cost modeling\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Rewrite `vegas_scan.py` with SQLite persistence (signals_log, positions_log, trades_log, performance_log)\n2. Add Sharpe Ratio > 1.8 + MDD < 20% as mathematical gatekeepers before outputting BUY signals\n3. Implement friction cost modeling: 0.15% per US stock trade (US_STOCK_COST = 0.0015)\n4. Add NL2Code JSON validation layer for signal outputs (prevent hallucinations in structured output)\n5. Upgrade `us_scan_live.py` signal labels to use Sharpe/MDD criteria instead of simple 🟢🟡⚪ scoring\n6. Add weekly auto-backtest mechanism to re-validate signals stored in SQLite\n\n## Critical Context\n- **Tina's core principles**: AI = strategy proposer not decision maker; Sharpe Ratio > 1.8 + MDD < 20% as mathematical gatekeepers; US friction cost = 0.15%, TW friction cost = 0.54%\n- **Tina's three SQLite tables**: `wisdom_logs` (AI proposals + reflections), `backtest_reports` (sharpe/mdd/total_return/win_rate), `sop_versions` (versioned SOP records)\n- **Current scripts in Ray's workspace**:\n  - `C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\us_scan_live.py` — live quotes with KDJ/MACD/MA\n  - `C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\us_momentum.py` — momentum rankings\n- **vegas_v1_live.py Telegram token**: `872054…qAiY` (Leo's bot, running outside OpenClaw)\n- **Tina PDF path**: `C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\media\\inbound\\tina_integrated_script_final---d364ed50-6095-4799-98ef-eb17e9c778b0.pdf`\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Original Request\nJo requested Option C: a complete Tina architecture refactoring for their trading system, including SQLite data persistence, backtest engine with risk gates, NL2Code validation, and an autonomous learning cycle.\n\n## Early Progress\n- Assistant recognized this as substantial work requiring a structured plan\n- Decided to use `update_plan` to track the work properly\n- Spawned a sub-agent to handle implementation while explaining the architecture to Jo\n\n## Context for Suffix\nThe assistant has created a multi-step plan covering: TinaDataCenter (SQLite with 4 log tables), TinaEngine (backtest with 0.15% friction costs + Sharpe > 1.5 + MDD < 15% gates), NL2Code validation layer, autonomous learning cycle, and refactoring of vegas_scan.py, us_momentum.py, us_scan_live.py scripts. Also plans to update SOUL.md/IDENTITY.md to reflect Ray's new architecture role.\n\n<read-files>\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\leo\\scripts\\leo_autonomous_cycle.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\leo\\scripts\\leo_autonomous_develop.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\tina_v3_alpha\\_cron_live_scan.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\vegas_v1_alpha\\_run_live_scan.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\vegas_v1_alpha\\tina_v3_core.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\vegas_v1_alpha\\tina_v3_scoring.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\vegas_v1_alpha\\tina_v3_sop.md\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\vegas_v1_alpha\\vegas_v1_live.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\Downloads\\tina_integrated_script_final.pdf\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\us_momentum.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\us_scan_live.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\vegas_scan.py\n</modified-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"8532acc1","tokensBefore":158179,"details":{"readFiles":["C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\leo\\scripts\\leo_autonomous_cycle.py","C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\leo\\scripts\\leo_autonomous_develop.py","C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\tina_v3_alpha\\_cron_live_scan.py","C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\vegas_v1_alpha\\_run_live_scan.py","C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\vegas_v1_alpha\\tina_v3_core.py","C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\vegas_v1_alpha\\tina_v3_scoring.py","C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\vegas_v1_alpha\\tina_v3_sop.md","C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\vegas_v1_alpha\\vegas_v1_live.py","C:\\Users\\USER\\Downloads\\tina_integrated_script_final.pdf"],"modifiedFiles":["C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\us_momentum.py","C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\us_scan_live.py","C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\vegas_scan.py"]},"fromHook":false}
