{"type":"message","id":"58e2059d","parentId":"3d6bc3b5","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:54:00.788Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The download is making progress - now at ~12MB/986MB with ~1.8MB/s speed, estimated 8 minutes 51 seconds. Much faster than before. Let me check back in a few minutes.\n\nFor now, let me answer Jo's question about what the local Qwen can do, since the model is not yet ready.\n","thinkingSignature":"072f417581a2d38f6a6911122ab34ee1801e798bf00a5dca4118bf22759fd85e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n還沒，網速有改善但仍在下載中：\n\n```\nqwen2.5:1.5b — 12MB/986MB (1%) @ 1.8MB/s，預計約 8-9 分鐘完成\n```\n\n---\n\n### 目前狀態\n\n模型還在下載，**現在還不能用**。Ollama 服務已就緒，但模型檔案未到位。\n\n---\n\n### 模型下好後能做的事\n\nQwen2.5:1.5B 雖然是 1.5B 參數的小模型，但對量化交易很有用：\n\n**1. 策略提案（NL2Code 驗證）**\n```\n輸入：RSI=28, Sharpe=1.8, MACD 金叉, 外資持續買超\n輸出：{\"strategy_name\":\"EMA_CROSS_12_26\",...}\n```\n\n**2. 市場情緒解讀**\n```\n輸入：NVDA 技術數據 + 新聞情緒摘要\n輸出：JSON 格式策略建議（溫度 0.1，輸出穩定）\n```\n\n**3. 快速本地推理（完全離線）**\n- 不走 API，省錢、完全隱私\n- 回測結果可以用本地模型做歸因分析\n\n**4. 自動化節流**\n- 高頻訊號用本地 1.5B（秒級響應）\n- 深度分析可以切換 7B（需要另外下載）\n\n---\n\n### 等模型下好後，測試指令\n\n```bash\nollama run qwen2.5:1.5b \"輸出一個 JSON 策略格式\"\n```\n\n或等我主動通知你。我每 5 分鐘檢查一次進度，下載完成後立刻測試並告訴你結果。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5200,"output":448,"cacheRead":98688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104336,"cost":{"input":0.00156,"output":0.0005376,"cacheRead":0.005921279999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.008018879999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778525864874,"responseId":"065159aee6288caa7d38687d0a5c30ba"}}
