{"type":"message","id":"d7fd6057","parentId":"0eb37437","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:54:00.788Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, 7B is downloading at 3.5MB/s, ~21 minutes. Let me report to Jo.\n","thinkingSignature":"5106abcf401b042f0bc28843e1358ba8af26482fde791b81594c4ae1a1bb0bcf"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**Qwen 7B 正在下載中：**\n\n```\nqwen2.5:7b — 344MB / 4.7GB (7%) @ 3.5MB/s，預計 ~21 分鐘\n```\n\n---\n\n**大腦分工已設定：**\n\n```\n本地 Python 脚本（不需要 LLM）\n├── us_momentum.py     → 動能計算\n├── us_scan_live.py    → 即時技術指標\n├── ray_data_center.py → SQLite 持久化\n├── ray_engine.py      → 回測 + 數學把關（Sharpe/MDD）\n└── ray_nl2code.py     → JSON Schema 驗證\n\nQwen 1.5B（ray-v1）— 快速響應 < 5 秒\n├── 即時策略提案（通過把關的信號 → JSON）\n├── 高頻篩選（每輪掃描）\n└── nl2code 格式最終確認\n\nQwen 7B（ray-deep-v1）— 深度推理\n├── 回測歸因分析（為何策略有效/失效）\n├── 市場情緒解讀\n├── 策略進化學習（RayEvolutionCore）\n└── 複雜投資組合建議\n```\n\n下載完成後我會建立 `ray-deep-v1` 模型並通知你。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":812,"output":304,"cacheRead":111680,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112796,"cost":{"input":0.00024359999999999999,"output":0.0003648,"cacheRead":0.0067008,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0073092}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778526754554,"responseId":"06515d26c91a45ac1cfac502f9340a8d"}}
