{"type":"message","id":"f4683c42","parentId":"061aa59f","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:54:00.788Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Everything is working now. Let me summarize the current state:\n\n1. **DB Fixed** - SQLite writes now work properly with `isolation_level=None` + explicit commit\n2. **NL2Code auto_correct** - Now fixes strategy_name and indicator automatically\n3. **ray_brain.py** - Full integration working: local indicators → math gate → Qwen 1.5B → DB\n4. **Qwen 7B** - Still downloading (2.2GB/4.7GB at last check)Let me provide a clear summary to Jo.\n","thinkingSignature":"18e46558a5b813d85aa28ae02fe5141b9ac7da3e117da15fda091964881616f3"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n✅ **系統整合完成，全部正常運行！**\n\n---\n\n### 最終狀態\n\n```\nDB 寫入：✅ 正常（isolation_level=None + 顯式 commit）\nNL2Code：✅ 自動修正（strategy_name、indicator、stop_loss、entry_condition）\n1.5B 提案：✅ 正常運行（NVDA/AMD/META 測試成功）\n7B 下載：⏳ 進行中（~47%，預計還有約 1.5 小時）\n```\n\n---\n\n### 實測結果\n\n```\nscan_and_propose(['NVDA', 'AMD', 'META']):\n\nBUY  NVDA  price=$219.39  score=4  strategy=FASTLOGIC（Sharpe=6.4, MDD=9.6%, WIN=70%）\nBUY  AMD   price=$457.39  score=4  strategy=FASTLOGIC\nWATCH META price=$599.29  score=1  strategy=FASTLOGICUNIT\n\nDB Stats: 6 signals total, 5 approved\n```\n\n---\n\n### 記憶系統升級（2026-05-12 重構）\n\n```\nray_data_center.py     — SQLite WAL 模式，7 張表（+ wisdom_logs）\nray_engine.py          — 0.15% 摩擦成本，Sharpe>1.5 / MDD<15% 把關\nray_nl2code.py         — auto_correct=True，自動修正 5 種常見錯誤\nray_evolution.py       — 11 種策略網格搜索，自動寫入 wisdom_logs\nray_brain.py           — 三層分工：本地計算 → 1.5B 提案 → 7B 歸因\nBRAIN_DIVISION.md     — 大腦分工藍圖文件\n```\n\n7B 下載完成後我會自動建立 `ray-deep-v1` 模型並跑深度歸因測試。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":132,"output":524,"cacheRead":167424,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":168080,"cost":{"input":0.0000396,"output":0.0006288,"cacheRead":0.01004544,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.010713839999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":17