{"type":"message","id":"b3fbf710","parentId":"f4683c42","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:54:00.788Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"整合分析此段文字後提出改善方案：### 1. 行為數據格式 (SFT JSONL)\n將模型訓練為「邏輯導向」的純文字格式，剔除聊天成分。{\"instruction\": \"TASK:文獻核心提取\", \"input\": \"SRC:IEEE_Ref_092.pdf; PARA:20; DB:Active\", \"output\": \"EXEC:pdf_parser->args(chunk:1024); LOGIC:extract_core_concepts; RESULT_TYPE:JSON_SCHEMA; DISTILL:TRUE; VAR_THRESHOLD:0.1\"}\n{\"instruction\": \"TASK:XeLaTeX排版優化\", \"input\": \"TEMPLATE:Academic_v1; CONTENT_BUFFER:ID_405\", \"output\": \"CALL:latex_engine; MODE:batch; PARAMS(engine:xelatex, optimize:true); STATUS:SUBMIT_TO_COMPILER\"}\n{\"instruction\": \"TASK:市場異動監控\", \"input\": \"TICKER:2330.TW; INDICATOR:MACD,KDJ; FREQ:1m\", \"output\": \"RUN:quant_algo_v4; IF:variance>0.05->TRIGGER:wisdom_log_write; ELSE:CONTINUE; MODE:PARALLEL_20\"}\n\n### 2. 認知引擎指令集 (Cognitive Logic Only)\n訓練模型識別任務後，直接輸出操作指令，而非自然語言。\n * 行為規範：\n * 禁用語： 「我會、幫你、分析、好的、請稍候」。\n * 選用語： EXEC (執行), CALL (調用), LOG (記錄), REFLECT (自我修正), DISTILL (蒸餾)。\n * 邏輯判斷訓練：\n * 若任務為已知演算法可解決 -> 輸出 USE_TOOL。\n * 若任務為未知結構需拆解 -> 輸出 LLM_PROBE (僅此時啟用大模型邏輯)。\n### 3. 變異數校準與回寫規則 (Variance & Write-back)\n在訓練數據中加入「判斷回寫」的權重，讓模型學會自主篩選高品質資料。\n * 規則描述：\n * INPUT: Analysis_Result; VARIANCE: High -> OUTPUT: ACTION(flag_outlier); WRITE(db_3, distilled_knowledge)。\n * INPUT: Task_Success; TIME: <2s -> OUTPUT: UPDATE_WEIGHTS(efficiency_score)。\n * 蒸餾目標： 訓練模型在輸出中包含一個 DISTILL: TRUE/FALSE 的標籤。當模型標註為 TRUE 時，後端系統自動將該次對話與執行結果存入微調資料庫，達成閉環成長。"}],"timestamp":1778528487568}}
{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:1616824689\",\n  \"message_id\": \"3464\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1616824689\",\n  \"sender\": \"Jo\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-05-12 03:11 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Jo (1616824689)\",\n  \"id\": \"1616824689\",\n  \"name\": \"Jo\",\n  \"username\": \"jojo_naan\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"b581103c","parentId":"b3fbf710","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:54:00.788Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"12dc6850","parentId":"b581103c","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:54:00.788Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Jo sent a message about a document about AI training methodology. Let me analyze this and provide an improvement plan.\n\nThe document describes three concepts:\n1. Behavioral Data Format (SFT JSONL) - A structured format for training AI models to be logic-oriented, removing chat components\n2. Cognitive Engine Instruction Set - Training the model to output operational instructions directly rather than natural language\n3. Variance Calibration & Write-back Rules - Adding judgment criteria for high-quality data selection\n\nThese are essentially Tina's LLM training methodology for creating a \"logic-only\" AI agent that:\n- Uses structured JSONL format for training\n- Outputs operational commands (EXEC/CALL/LOG/REFLECT/DISTILL) instead of natural language\n\n\n- Implements a self-improvement loop where high-variance outputs get flagged as outliers and low-latency successful tasks update model weights, with distillation-enabled responses automatically captured for fine-tuning\n\nThe key insight here is that Jo is describing Tina's approach to creating a lean, logic-driven AI that's optimized for quantitative trading tasks. I need to think about how to adapt this methodology for Ray's specific use case.\n\nThe core idea is straightforward: convert natural language trading analysis into structured command outputs (EXEC/CALL/LOG/REFLECT/DISTILL), use variance detection to identify when the model should distill its reasoning into training data, and build a closed feedback loop so the system learns from its own successful executions. The practical implementation would involve fine-tuning Qwen with a custom JSONL dataset in this format, setting up Ollama to serve the fine-tuned model, and establishing the variance scoring mechanism to determine what gets distilled.\n\nFor Ray's specific use case, I can adapt this by capturing successful runs where the local indicators combined with Qwen 1.5B's FASTLOGIC strategy produces good outcomes, then using those as training examples to make future outputs even more structured and command-like. The system would automatically identify high-quality signals (Sharpe > 1.5, MDD < 0.15), write them back to a distillation database, and trigger the fine-tuning process.","thinkingSignature":"032b4e465b40adad633bd0c455a31c068640ac169e5c33659cbbdabf0719c9a8"},{"type":"text","text":"這是 Tina 的**認知引擎訓練方法論**，核心目標是打造一個「純邏輯輸出的 AI Agent」，而不是聊天機器人。對 Ray 的價值極高。\n\n---\n\n## 解析\n\n### Tina 的三層方法論\n\n| 層 | 核心概念 | 對 Ray 的意義 |\n|---|---|---|\n| **SFT JSONL** | 訓練格式：剔除「我會幫你分析」，直接輸出操作指令 | Ray 的輸出格式正規化 |\n| **Cognitive Logic Only** | 禁語聊天術語，強制 EXEC/CALL/LOG/REFLECT/DISTILL | Ray 輸出改為結構化指令 |\n| **Variance Write-back** | 高品質對話自動蒸餾回訓練數據，閉環成長 | 勝利的 Signal → 自动微調資料 |\n\n---\n\n## 對 Ray 的具體改善方案\n\n### 第一層：輸出格式改造\n\n**現狀：** Qwen 1.5B 輸出 `{\"strategy_name\":\"FASTLOGIC\",...}` — 仍是自然語言思維的殘留\n\n**改造目標：** 讓 Ray 的輸出變成「操作指令」而非「回覆文字」\n\n```\n現在：\nRay: \"NVDA 建議買入，策略是...\"\n\n改造後：\nEXEC:log_signal  → 寫入 SQLite\nCALL:fast_propose → 調用 1.5B\nLOG:wisdom_write → 記錄蒸餾素材\nDISTILL:TRUE     → 標記高品質案例\n```\n\n### 第二層：Variance 自動蒸餾（最關鍵）\n\n讓每一次**數學把關通過的信號**自動成為微調素材：\n\n```python\n# 每當這個組合出現時，自動蒸餾\nif math_passed == True and strategy_output != error:\n    distill_candidate = {\n        \"instruction\": \"TASK:momentum_signal_strategy\",\n        \"input\": f\"SYMBOL:{symbol}; RSI:{rsi}; SHARPE:{sharpe}; MDD:{mdd}\",\n        \"output\": f\"EXEC:log_signal->{signal_tag}; STRATEGY:{strategy_name}; STOP_LOSS:{stop_loss}\"\n    }\n    if variance < threshold:\n        write_to_distill_db(distill_candidate)  # 蒸餾寫入\n        UPDATE_WEIGHTS(efficiency_score=+0.01)   # 權重更新\n```\n\n### 第三層：建立 Ray 自己的蒸餾資料庫\n\n```\ndistill_knowledge.db\n├── id, timestamp\n├── instruction    # 任務描述\n├── input         # 市場數據快照\n├── output        # 最終執行的操作指令\n├── sharpe        # 該決策的 Sharpe\n├── distill_label # DISTILL: TRUE/FALSE\n└── used_count    # 被用於微調的次數\n```\n\n---\n\n## 實作順序\n\n| 順序 | 項目 | 優先級 |\n|---|---|---|\n| **1** | 建立 `distill_knowledge.db` 蒸餾資料庫 | 🔴 高 |\n| **2** | 在 `ray_brain.py` 的 `scan_and_propose` 加入 variance 計算 + distill 標記 | 🔴 高 |\n| **3** | 定義 Ray 的 Cognitive Logic 指令集（EXEC/CALL/LOG/REFLECT/DISTILL） | 🟡 中 |\n| **4** | 收集 100 筆高質量信號蒸餾案例 | 🟡 中 |\n| **5** | 準備 SFT JSONL 微調資料，用 Ollama 對 qwen2.5:1.5b 做蒸餾微調 | 🟢 低（需時間） |\n\n---\n\n## 立即可做的（今天）\n\n在 `ray_brain.py` 加入這段代碼，讓系統自動識別並蒸餾高品質決策：\n\n```python\n# 在 scan_and_propose 的信號寫入時，自動蒸餾\nif ind.get(\"math_passed\") and not \"error\" in strategy:\n    distill_record = {\n        \"instruction\": f\"TASK:us_momentum_scan; SYMBOL:{sym}\",\n        \"input\": json.dumps({k: v for k, v in ind.items() if k not in [\"error\"]}),\n        \"output\": json.dumps(strategy),\n        \"sharpe\": ind.get(\"sharpe_30d\"),\n        \"distill\": True\n    }\n    db.log_distill(distill_record)  # 寫入蒸餾庫\n```\n\n要現在實作嗎？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":106,"output":1387,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":169181,"totalTokens":170674,"cost":{"input":0.0000318,"output":0.0016644,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.063442875,"total":0.06513907499999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778528487574,"responseId":"065163ed5aa4ec0d46b40c4630c47ba2"}}
