{"type":"message","id":"272e40ea","parentId":"105e5233","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:54:00.788Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to create the memory directory and file. But the write tool is restricted. Let me use the proper path.\n","thinkingSignature":"410ce4ff5698174b5892fdadd2677878fa2ce0d21594845186287bd676f4b2d4"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ll4il4rnbeqx_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Memory 2026-05-12 — Ray Agent\n\n## 安裝與設定\n\n### Qwen 模型\n- Ollama 0.23.1 已安裝 ✅\n- qwen2.5:1.5b 已下載 ✅ (ray-v1 Modelfile 已創建)\n- qwen2.5:7b 下載中（約 47%，預計還需 ~1.5 小時）\n\n### 蒸餾框架（今日完成）\n- ray_distiller.py 已建立（未執行）\n- 目標：Sharpe > 1.8 的黃金案例 → JSONL → 微調 1.5B\n\n### 數據庫現況\n- wisdom_logs: 0 筆（還沒有實際蒸餾數據）\n- backtest_reports: 還沒有實際執行過\n- signals_log: 有一些掃描數據\n\n### 腳本狀態\n- ray_data_center.py ✅（isolation_level=None + 顯式 commit）\n- ray_engine.py ✅\n- ray_nl2code.py ✅（auto_correct=True）\n- ray_evolution.py ✅\n- ray_brain.py ✅\n- ray_distiller.py ✅（已建立但未執行）\n\n### 待執行\n1. ray_distiller.py → 生成 ray_distill_train.jsonl\n2. Qwen 7B 下載完成 → 建立 ray-deep-v1\n3. Ray KAL 自學循環測試\n4. Unsloth 安裝 + 微調 1.5B","path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\memory\\2026-05-12.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":176,"output":400,"cacheRead":84480,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85056,"cost":{"input":0.000052799999999999996,"output":0.00047999999999999996,"cacheRead":0.005068799999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005601599999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778528871353,"responseId":"0651656c42a091af601fe1ed1d666249"}}
