{"type":"message","id":"0c4c28b3","parentId":"ab21783e","timestamp":"2026-05-11T20:00:39.928Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants a distillation pipeline. I've created:\n1. `ray_gold_miner.py` - Gold sample extractor\n2. `ray_logic_aligner.py` - Logic alignment (7B as tutor, 1.5B as student)\n\nNow I should check the OpenClaw config to understand how to route calls to MiniMax vs local Qwen, and also see if I can set up some kind of automatic triggering for these pipelines.\n\nLet me also check what files exist in the ray agent directory now to clean up temporary files.\n","thinkingSignature":"f5fdddb00d54478db1a6260d2b62f8d5b3e00a5c59b26d9fbdc98e1293cc6ed5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d2mz8w005b2c_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem \"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\" -File | Where-Object {$_.Name -match \"^(check_list|test|update_key|write_scan|shioaji|test_finmind|test_sox|test_yf)\"} | Select-Object Name, Length","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2176,"output":209,"cacheRead":126016,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128401,"cost":{"input":0.0006527999999999999,"output":0.00025079999999999997,"cacheRead":0.007560959999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00846456}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778529633242,"responseId":"06516863ce5a52e58ddbdaba09e1b698"}}
