{"type":"message","id":"0d724b21","parentId":"1d7786b0","timestamp":"2026-05-11T20:02:43.467Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The qwen2.5:7b model is still downloading at 52%, about 1h16m remaining. That's fine. Let me provide a status update about all the distillation scripts that have been created and what needs to happen next.\n","thinkingSignature":"20dd7ab82cf6c5a05faa415a1c2c54a086bb634fc0ead521f98174c5ba8ce909"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**✅ 蒸餾管線已建立完成（所有腳本已就緒）**\n\n---\n\n## 建立的腳本\n\n| 腳本 | 功能 | 狀態 |\n|---|---|---|\n| `ray_gold_miner.py` | 黃金樣本篩選（Sharpe>1.8/MDD<12%/Win>45%/Trades>20）| ✅ 完成 |\n| `ray_logic_aligner.py` | 7B 導師批改 1.5B → 修正蒸餾對 | ✅ 完成 |\n| `ray_train_tina.py` | Unsloth 微調 1.5B（LoRA rank=32/batch=2/GA=4）| ✅ 完成 |\n| `BRAIN_DIVISION.md` | 更新分工藍圖（蒸餾管線版）| ✅ 完成 |\n\n---\n\n## 7B 下載進度\n\n```\nqwen2.5:7b — 52% (2.4GB/4.7GB) @ 490KB/s，預計 1h16m\n```\n\n---\n\n## 下一步（等 7B 下好）\n\n```bash\n# 1. 等 7B 下好 → 建立 ray-deep-v1 Modelfile\n# 2. 建立因果蒸餾數據\npython ray_gold_miner.py\n\n# 3. Logic Alignment（7B 批改 1.5B）\npython ray_logic_aligner.py\n\n# 4. 安裝 Unsloth + 微調\npip install unsloth\npython ray_train_tina.py --mode causal_sft --epochs 3\n\n# 5. 合併並匯出 Ollama\nollama create ray-tina-v1 -f TinaModelfile\n```\n\n**整個蒸餾管線現在已準備就緒，只等 7B 下好就可以開始跑了。**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":293,"output":450,"cacheRead":132608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":133351,"cost":{"input":0.0000879,"output":0.00054,"cacheRead":0.00795648,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00858438}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778529749377,"responseId":"065168d80c757e6933ab267533d2c85b"}}
